Dialogue: 0.0:00:31.84.0:00:33.31.Default..0.0.0..Juju Scroll.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:33.45.0:00:34.60.Default..0.0.0..Movie Version.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:34.65.0:00:36.02.Default..0.0.0..JUJU SCROLL\NMOVIE VERSION
Dialogue: 0.0:00:41.16.0:00:43.17.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..I heard that if you eat mochi\Nbefore going to see a movie.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:43.17.0:00:45.49.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..it makes you less likely to go to the bathroom during.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:45.80.0:00:49.01.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..Huh? I heard eating plenty of salt was good for that.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:49.37.0:00:50.88.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..Want some popcorn?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:51.79.0:00:54.35.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..I told you to get the caramel kind!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:54.35.0:00:57.44.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..You didn't contribute a single yen.\Nso you don't get any right to decide.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:57.73.0:00:59.67.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..That's outrageous!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:59.67.0:01:00.86.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..Oh. HR! Oh. HR!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:00.86.0:01:02.34.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..The power harassment here is awful.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:02.34.0:01:04.04.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..so send a different long-haired guy.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:04.21.0:01:06.05.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..One you might find working in a beauty parlor!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:06.66.0:01:09.35.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..- Send a different wannabe host too.\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:09.73.0:01:11.86.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..By the way.\Nthe theory is that you're less.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:11.86.0:01:14.66.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..likely to use the bathroom because the digest of mochi produces
Dialogue: 0.0:01:14.71.0:01:17.01.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..glycogen. which draws water into cells.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:17.01.0:01:18.06.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..but there's no proof to it.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:18.39.0:01:19.48.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..That's our witch doctor for you!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:19.69.0:01:21.68.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..I hope you get sent to Black Jack!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:21.99.0:01:25.91.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..Black Jack graduated medical school.\Nso why is he unlicensed anyway?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:26.01.0:01:30.07.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..I guess we'll learn the answer to that in this movie.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:30.46.0:01:33.23.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..Believe me or don't. it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:33.59.0:01:37.28.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..I should probably mention that the "witch" part \Nof "witch doctor" also refers to actual jujutsu sorcery.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:38.37.0:01:40.08.JUJU SANPO..0.0.0..Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:02.70.0:02:05.13.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}Things were busy that summer.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:06.12.0:02:10.46.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}The frequent disasters of the \Npast year probably played a role.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:11.25.0:02:13.61.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}but cursed spirits were \Nspringing up like maggots.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:42.71.0:02:45.08.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}Exorcise. absorb.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:45.08.0:02:46.64.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}Over and over.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:51.38.0:02:52.36.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}Exorcise.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:52.93.0:02:53.90.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}Absorb.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:55.16.0:02:56.52.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}No one else understands
Dialogue: 0.0:02:57.22.0:02:58.82.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}what cursed spirits taste like.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:00.79.0:03:05.06.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}It's like swallowing a dirty rag that's \Nbeen used to clean up shit and vomit.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:05.93.0:03:06.90.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}Exorcise.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:07.70.0:03:08.87.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}Absorb.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:10.13.0:03:13.25.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}"What I witnessed isn't uncommon."
Dialogue: 0.0:03:13.25.0:03:15.19.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}"I understood the ugliness of the masses.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:15.94.0:03:21.60.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}and still chose to be a \Njujutsu sorcerer who saves others."
Dialogue: 0.0:03:23.66.0:03:27.34.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}That's what I've been telling \Nmyself ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:28.27.0:03:29.61.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..{\i1}Ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:30.59.0:03:32.63.Italics..0.0.0..JUNE 6TH 2006
Dialogue: 0.0:03:34.11.0:03:38.42.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Apparently. this used to be \Nthe home of the president
Dialogue: 0.0:03:38.42.0:03:42.02.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..of a company managing a local \Nchain of barbecue restaurants.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:42.81.0:03:45.52.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..However. in July of last year.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:45.52.0:03:51.18.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..the mad cow disease breakout dealt \Na fatal blow to his restaurants.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:51.18.0:03:54.70.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..so he committed suicide with his family \Nafter they were buried under vast debt.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:54.70.0:03:58.66.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..From then on. local rumors claimed \Nthe president's home was haunted.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:58.93.0:04:01.67.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..so local school kids. college students \Nfrom outside the prefecture.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:02.09.0:04:05.26.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..job-hoppers. and others would visit \Nit as part of a test of courage.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:05.26.0:04:07.13.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..and subsequently go missing.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:08.88.0:04:10.76.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Those rumors brought about more rumors.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:10.76.0:04:12.85.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..and the damage just continued to spread.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:13.62.0:04:18.18.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Rumors do tend to spread rather \Nquickly around haunted spots.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:18.52.0:04:24.68.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..They can spread at an unbelievable \Npace nowadays. thanks to the Internet.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:24.68.0:04:29.45.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..This all just means even more \Nwork for us jujutsu sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:30.08.0:04:35.21.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..In addition to that. three grade school kids \Nwent missing on their way home from school.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:35.21.0:04:38.70.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..There's also a high chance \Nthe families. police. colleagues.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:38.70.0:04:42.46.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..and friends who trace the paths \Nof those who disappeared
Dialogue: 0.0:04:42.46.0:04:44.82.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..will reach the mansion and \Nbecome victims themselves.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:45.46.0:04:48.71.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..We have to sever the root of \Nthis issue as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:49.85.0:04:54.29.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..HQ sent us to investigate because \Nthey reached the same conclusion.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:52.05.0:04:57.05.Default.Sign.0.0.0..{\fad(1000.1000)}Warning!\N{\fs20\c&H393542&\3c&H727051&}Entering These Premises Is Forbidden!\NMany Have Gone Missing!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:55.01.0:04:57.67.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..They're even paying my fees. \Nwhich aren't cheap.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:58.50.0:05:00.69.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Did you overcharge them again?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:01.01.0:05:03.16.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..You make it sound so bad.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:03.16.0:05:05.46.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Call it negotiation.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:06.12.0:05:07.34.Default.Assistant Supervisor.0.0.0..We're here.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:08.18.0:05:10.14.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Let's go. then.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:11.23.0:05:15.53.Default.Screen.0.0.0..JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0.0:05:15.53.0:05:17.90.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Emerge from darkness. blacker than darkness.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:17.90.0:05:19.09.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Purify that—
Dialogue: 0.0:05:19.86.0:05:21.62.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..There's no need for a veil.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:21.62.0:05:22.54.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:23.54.0:05:26.00.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..I don't sense the presence of any Curses.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:26.00.0:05:29.83.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..The cause is almost certainly \Ninside the building.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:30.56.0:05:34.58.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..You can cast the veil later if we \Nend up attacking it from outside.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:35.09.0:05:36.30.Default.Screen.0.0.0..{\fad(175.0)\fnComic Sans MS\fs12\fsp2\c&H302510&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\bord1\3a&H60&\pos(242.667.200)}...True.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:37.42.0:05:38.51.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..It's unlocked.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:39.72.0:05:41.70.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Seems like something's blocking the door.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:45.29.0:05:46.47.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..What is all this?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:50.85.0:05:52.01.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Mei-san.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:53.02.0:05:54.10.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..It's here.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:54.86.0:05:56.65.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..And it's all around us. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:02.49.0:06:04.41.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:04.41.0:06:07.25.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..I don't need that. but you do. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:08.10.0:06:10.57.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:12.21.0:06:13.75.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..All right.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:24.47.0:06:27.26.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..I-Incredible.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:29.62.0:06:32.01.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Oh. it still has electricity.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:33.25.0:06:36.56.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..For now. let's have a \Nlook inside the building.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:36.80.0:06:38.37.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..I'll take this floor.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:38.37.0:06:40.04.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..you take the second.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:40.04.0:06:42.57.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Huh? All by myself?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:42.57.0:06:44.27.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Is there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:44.27.0:06:47.90.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..N-No. i-it's fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:47.90.0:06:49.65.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Off you go. then.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:52.98.0:06:54.10.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:36.68.0:07:38.34.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..This is the last one.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:27.02.0:08:29.86.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..You could be the next big Scream Queen.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:32.87.0:08:33.94.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Jeez!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:33.94.0:08:36.34.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Please don't startle me like that!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:36.84.0:08:39.44.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..You got startled all on your own.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:40.22.0:08:43.11.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Are you done exploring the first floor?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:46.12.0:08:47.82.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..This is the first floor.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:49.06.0:08:49.83.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:50.56.0:08:53.62.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..I was walking down \Nthe first floor hallway.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:54.10.0:08:56.02.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..What? But...
Dialogue: 0.0:08:56.49.0:09:01.74.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..I know I entered a room \Nat the end of the hallway...
Dialogue: 0.0:09:03.08.0:09:04.79.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..A box of candy.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:05.00.0:09:06.93.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..A bag of potato chips.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:07.44.0:09:07.97.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Cans.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:08.38.0:09:09.81.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..A backpack.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:10.14.0:09:11.47.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..A sweatshirt.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:12.87.0:09:15.28.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..I've already seen this three times.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:16.00.0:09:21.26.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..And see these marks? I made \Nthem on my way through here.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:22.66.0:09:27.50.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..It would seem that we're already \Nin the belly of the beast.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:27.50.0:09:29.73.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:35.16.0:09:36.86.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..For real?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:39.11.0:09:42.96.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..How long {\i1}is{\i0} this hallway?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:44.22.0:09:46.12.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..We've been moving for thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:46.12.0:09:48.38.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..so about four kilometers so far.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:49.28.0:09:52.34.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..It's not an innate domain. is it?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:52.90.0:09:54.12.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..It's not.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:54.40.0:09:57.48.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Those are manifestations \Nof the spirit's mindscape.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:58.02.0:09:59.42.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Which means...
Dialogue: 0.0:09:59.69.0:10:01.18.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..This is a barrier.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:01.60.0:10:02.77.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Correct.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:03.00.0:10:06.41.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Most likely. the victims \Nwere trapped inside this
Dialogue: 0.0:10:06.41.0:10:08.51.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..and then killed by the cursed spirit.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:11.26.0:10:13.86.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Though. considering the \Nuse of this technique.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:13.86.0:10:16.45.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..the cursed spirit itself should be weak.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:17.26.0:10:20.36.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..So if we can just escape this barrier...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:23.17.0:10:25.04.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Now. quiz time.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:25.04.0:10:28.41.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..How would you break this. Utahime?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:32.90.0:10:35.18.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..This hallway is repeating itself.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:35.18.0:10:37.02.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..At first...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:40.50.0:10:42.07.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..I thought...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:42.66.0:10:44.38.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..I'm surprised you could touch them.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:44.38.0:10:47.24.Default.Utahime.0.0.0.....it was shaped like a donut.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:47.86.0:10:51.34.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..But we passed by four of \Nthe marks you made. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:51.74.0:10:54.99.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..When I calculated how many \Npaces apart they were. I got...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:54.99.0:10:56.60.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..122.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:56.60.0:10:57.74.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..203.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:57.74.0:10:59.06.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..157.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:59.06.0:10:59.99.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..and 270 paces.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:00.59.0:11:04.34.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..So the spacing between marks was random.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:04.90.0:11:05.96.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..I see.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:06.46.0:11:10.51.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..The interval between \Nrepetitions isn't standardized.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:11.06.0:11:14.02.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Which means that. most likely...
Dialogue: 0.0:11:14.02.0:11:17.10.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..this barrier is patching spaces together.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:17.71.0:11:22.68.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..So if we both run down the hallway \Nat top speed. then at some point...
Dialogue: 0.0:11:26.79.0:11:27.78.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..It'll break.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:29.75.0:11:31.69.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Close. Ninety points.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:31.69.0:11:32.70.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..D'oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:33.21.0:11:34.94.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..What's the remaining ten?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:35.66.0:11:40.83.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..When we run. we do so in opposite \Ndirections at the same time.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:40.83.0:11:42.37.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..I get it!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:42.37.0:11:44.43.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..So my patching theory was correct.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:44.43.0:11:47.20.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..and if we quickly advance \Nin different directions.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:47.20.0:11:50.49.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..that makes it harder for the cursed \Nspirit to hold the barrier together.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:50.49.0:11:53.49.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..And once we have that opening. \Nwe might be able to get out.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:53.49.0:11:54.64.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..One hundred points.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:54.64.0:11:56.14.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Then. with that settled...
Dialogue: 0.0:11:56.89.0:12:00.98.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..If this works. I'll be expecting a promotion.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:01.60.0:12:03.85.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..How much do you have in savings?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:03.85.0:12:04.67.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:05.43.0:12:08.02.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Never mind. I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:08.02.0:12:09.08.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Right!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:09.71.0:12:13.44.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Okay... Ready. set...
Dialogue: 0.0:12:14.74.0:12:15.46.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Go!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:20.70.0:12:21.99.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..We did it!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:22.34.0:12:24.25.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Wait. wha—
Dialogue: 0.0:12:42.58.0:12:44.64.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I'm here to save you.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:46.90.0:12:48.36.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Utahime.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:57.86.0:13:02.62.Default.Screen.0.0.0..JUJUTSU KAISEN - HIDDEN INVENTORY\N/PREMATURE DEATH - MOVIE VERSION
Dialogue: 1.0:14:18.26.0:14:20.60.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..JUJUTSU HIGH\NSECOND YEAR\NSATORU GOJO
Dialogue: 0.0:14:19.16.0:14:20.60.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:20.60.0:14:22.54.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 1.0:14:20.60.0:14:25.81.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..SECOND GRADE\NSORCERER\NIORI UTAHIME
Dialogue: 0.0:14:22.54.0:14:23.77.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..And be more polite!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.77.0:14:25.81.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..If I was crying. would you console me?
Dialogue: 1.0:14:25.81.0:14:28.56.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..FIRST GRADE\NSORCERER\NMEI MEI
Dialogue: 0.0:14:26.41.0:14:28.56.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..I'd certainly appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:29.01.0:14:31.17.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Nah. you wouldn't cry. Mei-san.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:31.17.0:14:32.33.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You're strong.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:33.49.0:14:34.65.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..That so?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:35.69.0:14:38.32.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Gojo! You listen here!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:38.32.0:14:39.74.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..I don't need your hel—
Dialogue: 0.0:14:44.57.0:14:45.63.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Don't swallow it.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:46.19.0:14:47.65.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'll absorb it later.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:48.49.0:14:51.25.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru. it's not nice to pick on the weak.
Dialogue: 1.0:14:48.50.0:14:51.25.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..JUJUTSU HIGH\NSECOND YEAR\NGETO SUGURU
Dialogue: 0.0:14:51.46.0:14:54.49.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..What kind of idiot picks on the strong?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:55.25.0:14:58.86.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..You're the one fanning the flames \Nlike it comes naturally. Geto-kun.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:00.52.0:15:02.33.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Utahime-senpai!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:03.06.0:15:04.64.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:04.64.0:15:05.89.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Shoko!
Dialogue: 1.0:15:04.64.0:15:10.02.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..JUJUTSU HIGH\NSECOND YEAR\NIEIRI SHOKO
Dialogue: 0.0:15:05.89.0:15:08.01.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:08.01.0:15:10.02.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..We hadn't heard from you for two whole days.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:10.02.0:15:13.02.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Shoko!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:13.35.0:15:17.95.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Shoko! Don't let yourself \Nturn out like those two!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:17.95.0:15:20.94.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..I won't turn into trash like them.
Dialogue: 1.0:15:19.53.0:15:25.83.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..SAID TRASH
Dialogue: 0.0:15:20.94.0:15:24.01.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The path Utahime walked is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:24.01.0:15:25.51.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Shut up.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:25.83.0:15:28.53.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..Wait. two days?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:29.32.0:15:33.62.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Ah. was the cursed spirit's barrier \None of those that messes with time?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:33.62.0:15:35.84.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..They're rare. but they \Ndo happen now and then.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:35.84.0:15:38.73.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I thought it was odd. \Nsince Mei-san was with you.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:39.21.0:15:40.81.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..Seems like it was.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:41.98.0:15:42.94.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Something the matter?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:43.42.0:15:47.35.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..No. Just realized that means \Nit was actually two days' labor.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:47.35.0:15:52.03.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..and that means extra fees paid out to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:52.03.0:15:54.44.Default.Utahime.0.0.0..She's planning to overcharge again.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:54.44.0:15:57.57.Default.Mei Mei.0.0.0..That aside. what about the veil. you three?
Dialogue: 1.0:16:01.57.0:16:05.38.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Next. the explosion that occurred \Nyesterday in Hamamatsu. Shizuoka.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:05.34.0:16:08.54.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..One of you three said they \Nwould cast the veil themselves
Dialogue: 0.0:16:08.54.0:16:11.87.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..and left your assistant \Nsupervisor behind. didn't you?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:11.87.0:16:14.41.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..And then you forgot the veil.
Dialogue: 1.0:16:11.88.0:16:14.42.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..FIRST GRADE\NSORCERER\NYAGA MASAMICHI
Dialogue: 0.0:16:14.41.0:16:15.76.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Come forward.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:17.12.0:16:18.26.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Sensei!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:18.26.0:16:20.12.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Why don't we stop this hunt for the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:20.12.0:16:21.30.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..So it was you. Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:22.34.0:16:23.10.Default.Screen.0.0.0..DISCIPLINE
Dialogue: 0.0:16:23.87.0:16:28.34.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Is a veil that necessary in the first place?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:29.06.0:16:31.98.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..It's not like it matters if \Nnormies see or not. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:31.98.0:16:34.73.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..They can't see cursed spirits \Nor cursed techniques. anyway.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:37.48.0:16:39.41.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Of course it's not good for them to see.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:39.41.0:16:41.52.Default.Geto.0.0.0..The strongest deterrent \Nagainst the outbreak
Dialogue: 0.0:16:41.87.0:16:44.71.Default.Geto.0.0.0..of a cursed spirit is the \Nmental calm of the populace.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:45.22.0:16:48.51.Default.Geto.0.0.0..That's exactly why we have to conceal
Dialogue: 0.0:16:48.51.0:16:51.20.Default.Geto.0.0.0..the threats they can't even \Nsee as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:51.56.0:16:52.56.Default.Geto.0.0.0..And that's not all—
Dialogue: 0.0:16:52.56.0:16:54.46.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Yeah. yeah. I get it.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:00.54.0:17:04.93.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Looking out for the weak \Nis so exhausting. honestly.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:05.57.0:17:07.19.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Survival of the weakest.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:07.19.0:17:09.76.Default.Geto.0.0.0..That's how a society should be.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:10.05.0:17:12.86.Default.Geto.0.0.0..The weak help each other and \Ndiscourage any who are too strong.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:13.06.0:17:14.43.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Listen. Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:14.71.0:17:18.01.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Jujutsu exists to protect \Nnon-jujutsu sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:19.01.0:17:20.81.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Is that your moral argument?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:21.17.0:17:24.03.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I hate moral arguments.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:24.56.0:17:25.40.Default.Geto.0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:26.07.0:17:29.12.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Assigning reasons and \Nresponsibility to strength
Dialogue: 0.0:17:29.12.0:17:31.83.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..is what those who are weak do.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:41.71.0:17:45.57.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Quit making yourself feel \Nbetter by spouting bullshit.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:45.93.0:17:47.69.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Blegh.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:47.69.0:17:49.50.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Run for it.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:49.84.0:17:52.77.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Want to take this outside. Satoru?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:52.77.0:17:54.81.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You feeling lonely?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:54.80.0:17:56.18.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:58.98.0:18:00.91.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..How long are you going \Nto keep fooling around?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:01.26.0:18:02.57.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Where did Shoko go?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:02.77.0:18:03.91.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Who knows?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:03.91.0:18:05.07.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Bathroom. probably.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:05.95.0:18:07.07.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Whatever.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:07.07.0:18:09.90.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..This mission is being assigned to you two.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:11.01.0:18:12.83.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..What are those faces for?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:13.26.0:18:14.41.Default.Both.0.0.0..Nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:15.14.0:18:17.79.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Frankly. I think it's too much for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:18.21.0:18:20.24.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..but Tengen-sama asked for you specifically.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:22.22.0:18:24.09.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Your mission has two goals.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:24.38.0:18:25.99.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..The Star Plasma Vessel
Dialogue: 0.0:18:26.32.0:18:28.44.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..is the one compatible with Tengen-sama.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:28.44.0:18:32.56.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..You are to escort that girl and erase her.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:32.93.0:18:35.57.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Escort a brat and erase her?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:36.20.0:18:37.48.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..That's right.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:37.48.0:18:39.04.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Have you finally gone senile?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:39.24.0:18:40.82.Default.Geto.0.0.0..It is spring.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:40.82.0:18:43.57.Default.Geto.0.0.0..He's probably got his head full \Nwith being the next principal.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:44.09.0:18:45.34.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Jokes aside. though—
Dialogue: 0.0:18:45.34.0:18:48.37.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..{\an8}I'll be the one to decide \Nif I let that off as a joke.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:46.83.0:18:49.72.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Is this about renewing \NTengen-sama's technique?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:51.30.0:18:52.24.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..What's that?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:55.56.0:18:56.83.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:57.47.0:19:00.55.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Tengen-sama possesses the \Ncursed technique of Immortality.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:00.55.0:19:02.07.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..but it is not Eternal Youth.
Dialogue: 1.0:19:02.07.0:19:04.78.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..It wouldn't be an issue \Nif all he did was get older.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:04.78.0:19:07.13.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..but after his body ages to a certain point.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:07.13.0:19:09.88.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..the cursed technique \Nbegins rewriting his body.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:11.45.0:19:12.78.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Evolution.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:12.78.0:19:16.31.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..He'll cease to be human and become \Na higher form of existence.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:16.53.0:19:18.22.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:18.22.0:19:20.00.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Sounds cool.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:20.00.0:19:21.63.Default.Geto.0.0.0..According to Tengen-sama.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:21.63.0:19:25.67.Default.Geto.0.0.0..those who reach that state \Nof being have no will.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:25.97.0:19:29.07.Default.Geto.0.0.0..It means Tengen-sama would \Ncease to be Tengen-sama.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:29.07.0:19:30.82.Default - Copy..0.0.0..TOKYO JUJUTSU HIGH SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0.0:19:29.07.0:19:30.82.Default.Geto.0.0.0..All the jujutsu schools.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:30.82.0:19:33.27.Default.Geto.0.0.0..the barriers that form the \Nfoundation of jujutsu society.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:33.27.0:19:35.64.Default.Geto.0.0.0..the many barrier techniques \Nof the assistant supervisors...
Dialogue: 0.0:19:35.64.0:19:40.02.Default.Geto.0.0.0..They're all being strengthened by Tengen-sama.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:40.33.0:19:42.59.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Without the aid of his power.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:42.59.0:19:45.61.Default.Geto.0.0.0..we could hardly maintain security \Nor clean up after missions.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:45.96.0:19:47.42.Default.Geto.0.0.0..In the worst-case scenario.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:47.42.0:19:50.93.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Tengen-sama could even become \Na threat to mankind.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:50.93.0:19:54.25.Default.Geto.0.0.0..That's why. every 500 years. \Nhe finds the Plasma Star Vessel—
Dialogue: 0.0:19:54.52.0:19:57.65.Default.Geto.0.0.0..someone who is compatible with him—
Dialogue: 0.0:19:57.65.0:19:59.81.Default.Geto.0.0.0..and assimilates them. \Noverwriting the information of their body.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:00.21.0:20:02.05.Default.Geto.0.0.0..By renewing his body.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:02.05.0:20:04.57.Default.Geto.0.0.0..he resets his cursed \Ntechnique back to the start
Dialogue: 0.0:20:04.57.0:20:06.33.Default.Geto.0.0.0..and avoids Evolution.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:06.33.0:20:07.74.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I get it.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:07.74.0:20:10.29.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..It would be fine if he turned \Ninto MetalGreymon.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:10.29.0:20:12.78.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..but we can't have him \Nbecoming SkullGreymon.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:12.78.0:20:15.57.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So we have him start over from Koromon.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:16.33.0:20:19.05.Default.Geto.0.0.0..What? Yeah. sure. that works.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:19.05.0:20:23.36.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..The Star Plasma Vessel's \Nlocation has been leaked.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:23.36.0:20:27.64.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Right now. there are two major \Ngroups after the young girl's life.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:28.13.0:20:30.29.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..One is the Curse User Group Q.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:30.65.0:20:34.78.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..which seeks to upend jujutsu society \Nwith Tengen-sama's rampage.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:35.86.0:20:39.32.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..The other is the Star Religious \NGroup. also known as the
Dialogue: 0.0:20:39.32.0:20:42.16.Default.Yaga.0.0.0.."Time Vessel Association."\Nwhich worships Tengen-sama as a god.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:42.77.0:20:47.43.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Tengen-sama will assimilate the \NStar Plasma Vessel two days from now.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:47.43.0:20:52.30.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..You are to protect the girl until then and \Nensure that she reaches Tengen-sama!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:52.30.0:20:56.29.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..If you fail. the effects will ripple \Nthroughout even normal society!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.29.0:20:57.87.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:58.53.0:21:00.12.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Yeah. but you know.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:00.12.0:21:03.01.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I get why Curse User Group Q \Nwould be after her.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:03.01.0:21:06.30.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..but why would this Star Religious \NGroup want to kill a brat?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:06.92.0:21:10.17.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Their object of worship is \Nthe pure form of Tengen-sama.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:10.53.0:21:11.98.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Allowing the Star Plasma Vessel—
Dialogue: 0.0:21:11.98.0:21:15.73.Default.Geto.0.0.0..in their minds. an impurity—\Nto blend into him is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:16.52.0:21:19.37.Default.Geto.0.0.0..The Star Religious Group is an \Norganization of non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:19.37.0:21:21.51.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I don't think we need to pay them any mind.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:21.73.0:21:24.18.Default.Geto.0.0.0..The ones to be wary of are Q.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:24.47.0:21:26.35.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Well. I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:26.35.0:21:28.19.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..We're the strongest. after all.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:28.19.0:21:31.30.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..That's why Tengen-sama asked \Nfor us specifically. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:33.72.0:21:34.65.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..What is it?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:35.21.0:21:37.68.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You know. Satoru...
Dialogue: 0.0:21:37.68.0:21:39.97.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I've been wanting to say this for a while.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:39.97.0:21:42.50.Default.Geto.0.0.0..but you should stop being \Nso full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:42.81.0:21:44.33.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Huh?!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:45.30.0:21:48.09.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Especially when you're \Naddressing your superiors.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:48.09.0:21:50.69.Default.Geto.0.0.0..We might end up meeting \NTengen-sama. after all.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:50.69.0:21:54.34.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You should be more polite and humble.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:54.34.0:21:56.57.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You'd scare your juniors less. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:56.57.0:21:57.30.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Hah!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:57.54.0:21:58.89.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Screw that!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:58.89.0:22:01.04.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Come on. Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:01.04.0:22:02.26.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Whatever.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:02.26.0:22:03.81.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'll bring it up again later.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:08.45.0:22:09.43.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Coming.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:09.86.0:22:10.81.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:17.61.0:22:18.82.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..You alive?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:19.22.0:22:20.37.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I am. at least.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:21.32.0:22:24.33.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..You think we'll be blamed \Nif the brat died from that?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:25.23.0:22:25.62.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..{\pos(135.231)\b1\bord3\shad0\c&H000000&\3c&HE5E7E7&}Ah
Dialogue: 0.0:22:35.46.0:22:37.18.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:37.86.0:22:40.33.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..If you must hate someone. hate Tengen.
Dialogue: 1.0:22:38.30.0:22:41.56.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..Q\NCOMBATANT\NKOKUN
Dialogue: 0.0:22:40.81.0:22:41.56.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Wha—
Dialogue: 0.0:22:44.17.0:22:46.43.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Would you please stop making us stand out?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:46.43.0:22:48.52.Default.Geto.0.0.0..We just got chewed out \Nfor that this morning.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:49.27.0:22:50.98.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..So this girl is the Star Plasma Vessel?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:51.41.0:22:54.61.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..I know those uniforms. You're \Nsorcerers from Jujutsu High. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:54.61.0:22:56.07.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Hand over the kid.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:56.45.0:22:57.66.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Or I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:58.07.0:22:59.69.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:59.69.0:23:01.70.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Come closer and talk.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:02.09.0:23:04.43.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Man. barely safe.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:08.86.0:23:10.46.Default.Bayer.0.0.0..Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:11.02.0:23:13.46.Default.Bayer.0.0.0..You're Gojo Satoru. right?
Dialogue: 1.0:23:13.46.0:23:15.42.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..Q\NCOMBATANT\NBAYER
Dialogue: 0.0:23:13.75.0:23:15.46.Default.Bayer.0.0.0..You're famous.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:16.44.0:23:18.15.Default.Bayer.0.0.0..I hear you're strong.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:18.15.0:23:20.92.Default.Bayer.0.0.0..Let me find out if the rumors are true.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:21.46.0:23:24.77.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I'm down for that. but let's set some rules.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:24.77.0:23:25.98.Default.Bayer.0.0.0..Rules?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:26.45.0:23:29.41.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I don't want to get yelled \Nat for going overboard.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:29.68.0:23:32.82.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So if you cry and apologize. \NI won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:32.82.0:23:34.28.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..That's our rule.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:34.58.0:23:35.88.Default.Bayer.0.0.0..Damn brat.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:37.62.0:23:39.34.Default.Kong.0.0.0..It's started.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:40.29.0:23:44.00.Default.Kong.0.0.0..The Star Religious Group doesn't have the \Npower to fight against jujutsu sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:44.31.0:23:45.91.Default.Kong.0.0.0..But they can pay very well.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:45.91.0:23:47.69.Default.Kong.0.0.0..That I guarantee.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:48.70.0:23:50.05.Default.Kong.0.0.0..How about it. Zen'in?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:50.57.0:23:54.19.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Want to get in on the assassination \Nof the Star Plasma Vessel?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:54.90.0:23:56.98.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I'm not a Zen'in anymore.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:56.98.0:23:58.80.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I took my wife's name.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:59.14.0:24:00.77.Default.Toji.0.0.0..It's Fushiguro now.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:01.74.0:24:02.79.Default.Toji.0.0.0..But sure.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:03.17.0:24:05.04.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Count me in.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:35.12.0:24:36.45.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Please!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:36.45.0:24:38.04.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:38.04.0:24:39.75.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:39.75.0:24:40.75.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:40.75.0:24:41.95.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:42.34.0:24:43.75.Default.Curse.0.0.0..Let's kiss!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:43.75.0:24:44.13.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Huh?!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:44.13.0:24:47.17.Default.Curse.0.0.0..Let's kiss!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:47.72.0:24:49.68.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..I'll pull out of this job!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:49.68.0:24:51.34.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..I'll quit being a curse user. too!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:51.34.0:24:52.65.Default.Curse.0.0.0..Let's kiss!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:53.01.0:24:55.10.Default.Curse.0.0.0..C'mon. kiss!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:55.10.0:24:57.31.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Of course I'll quit Q. too!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:57.31.0:25:00.31.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..I know! I'll go back to the \Ncountryside and farm rice!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:02.27.0:25:03.73.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..I know you can hear me!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:04.52.0:25:07.28.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Like a curse user could cut it as a farmer.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:07.28.0:25:08.95.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..You {\i1}can{\i0} hear me!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:08.95.0:25:11.53.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Damn student acting all condescending!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:11.28.0:25:15.03.Default.Curse.0.0.0..{\an8}Lick. lick.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:11.53.0:25:13.87.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..But Bayer-san is here. too!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:13.87.0:25:16.20.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..He's Q's strongest combatant!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:17.04.0:25:19.00.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..He'll take care of you and these things!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:19.00.0:25:20.00.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:20.62.0:25:22.50.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Is this your "Bayer"?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:22.71.0:25:23.50.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:27.17.0:25:29.17.Default.Kokun.0.0.0..That's him.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:30.63.0:25:34.01.Default.Screen.0.0.0..Q\NDEPARTURE OF TOP COMBATANT.\N BAYER. LEADS TO ORGANIZATION'S COLLAPSE
Dialogue: 0.0:25:39.35.0:25:41.98.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}And all the boats are off at once.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:41.98.0:25:45.23.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}From the inside. we have Numbers \N1. 2. 4. 5. 3. and 6 starting the race.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:45.23.0:25:47.98.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}They're off with a beautiful straight shot.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:48.94.0:25:52.49.Default.Kong.0.0.0..And just what are you doing after \Nsuddenly disappearing on me?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:55.20.0:25:57.29.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Getting more money.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:57.95.0:26:00.87.Default.Kong.0.0.0..I've never seen you win once.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:01.21.0:26:02.87.Default.Kong.0.0.0..What about your job?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:03.58.0:26:05.29.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Oh. give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:05.29.0:26:07.92.Default.Toji.0.0.0..You're talking like I'm unemployed.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:09.71.0:26:11.21.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Because you are.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:11.60.0:26:16.60.Default.Kong.0.0.0..As a mediator. it's my duty to report \Nhow the job's going to the client.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:16.60.0:26:18.97.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I'm up against the Gojo clan's kid.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:18.97.0:26:22.39.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I wouldn't be able to do anything \Nif I just popped up in front of him.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:22.73.0:26:25.86.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I have to wear him down\Nusing some idiots first.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:26.21.0:26:27.94.Default.Toji.0.0.0..You go do your own damn job.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:27.94.0:26:29.73.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Already did. dumbass.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:29.73.0:26:33.75.Default.Kong.0.0.0..What were you thinking. \Nletting go of the entire deposit?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:34.45.0:26:36.53.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I told you. wearing him down.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:36.53.0:26:39.24.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Don't you worry. All that \Nmoney will come back to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:39.24.0:26:41.20.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Just like with this race.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:43.04.0:26:45.29.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Number 6. Hateno. crosses the line first!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:45.29.0:26:47.50.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Number 1. Doguchi. finishes next!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:47.50.0:26:49.67.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Following them in third is Number 2. Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:49.67.0:26:51.46.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}In fourth is Number 4. Nakaoka.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:50.21.0:26:51.30.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Tsk.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:51.46.0:26:53.30.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}In fifth is Number 3. Tanaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:26:51.46.0:26:54.72.Default.Kong.0.0.0..You're not cut out for making easy money.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:53.30.0:26:55.51.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}In sixth is Number 5. \NOkazaki. finishing last!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:55.51.0:26:59.93.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Number 6. Hateno. has given us an amazing \Ncomeback to watch in his first race!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:55.68.0:26:58.72.Default.Kong.0.0.0..I'm counting on you. Sorcerer Killer.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:59.93.0:27:01.43.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}That was our third race of the day.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:00.01.0:27:01.43.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Oh. right.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:02.10.0:27:03.56.Default.Kong.0.0.0..How's Megumi doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:15.41.0:27:16.57.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Who's that?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:18.08.0:27:20.13.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Should we get her to a doctor?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:20.44.0:27:24.59.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I wish I could use reverse \Ncursed energy like Shoko.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:24.59.0:27:26.09.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Yeah. that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:26.09.0:27:28.84.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I can't understand a word she says about it.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:29.12.0:27:31.39.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..You go "fwoo." then "hyoi."
Dialogue: 0.0:27:31.39.0:27:34.43.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Fwoo. hyoi. Get it?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:34.43.0:27:36.14.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..You've got no sense for this.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:40.94.0:27:42.15.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You're awake.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:51.20.0:27:52.24.Default.Riko.0.0.0..You scum!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:52.24.0:27:55.50.Default.Riko.0.0.0..If you want to kill me. \Nyou'll be the one to die first!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:57.96.0:27:59.92.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Riko-chan. calm down.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:59.92.0:28:03.44.Default.Geto.0.0.0..We're not with the group that attacked you.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:03.44.0:28:04.67.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Liar!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:04.67.0:28:06.09.Default.Riko.0.0.0..You have the face of a liar!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:06.09.0:28:07.80.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Your bangs are weird. too!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:14.39.0:28:19.14.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..GRIND
Dialogue: 0.0:28:15.56.0:28:17.39.Default.Riko.0.0.0..This is disrespectful!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:17.39.0:28:18.94.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..P-Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:18.94.0:28:20.15.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Kuroi!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:22.31.0:28:25.48.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Young lady. these men are our allies.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:26.36.0:28:29.57.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Kuroi. what are you riding on?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:29.95.0:28:32.70.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..This is thanks to Bangs Guy's technique.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:32.70.0:28:34.95.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Could you please not call me that?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:36.00.0:28:37.75.Default.Geto.0.0.0..It's Curse Manipulation.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:37.75.0:28:41.21.Default.Geto.0.0.0..As the name suggests. I can absorb \Nand manipulate cursed spirits.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:41.54.0:28:44.46.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..This brat is more aggressive \Nthan I expected.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:44.46.0:28:46.96.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I was trying to figure out \Nhow to be considerate.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:46.96.0:28:49.55.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..thinking she'd be more sentimental \Nabout the assimilation thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:49.93.0:28:50.88.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Hmph!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:50.88.0:28:53.68.Default.Riko.0.0.0..A commoner's way of thinking!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:53.68.0:28:54.51.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Huh?!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:54.51.0:28:55.30.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Listen up!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:57.64.0:29:02.02.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Tengen-sama is me. and I am Tengen-sama!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:02.02.0:29:05.82.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Some might mistake \Nassimilation for death. as you do.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:05.82.0:29:08.48.Default.Riko.0.0.0..but there's a big difference!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:08.74.0:29:11.78.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I might become Tengen-sama \Nthrough the assimilation.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:11.78.0:29:14.36.Default.Riko.0.0.0..but Tengen-sama will also become me!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:14.64.0:29:16.74.Default.Riko.0.0.0..My will! My heart!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:16.74.0:29:19.10.Default.Riko.0.0.0..My soul will continue to live \Non after the assimilation!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:19.10.0:29:20.25.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You changed your home screen?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:20.25.0:29:21.54.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..To Inoue Waka.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:21.54.0:29:22.71.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:23.21.0:29:26.34.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I bet you don't have many \Nfriends if you talk like that.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:26.34.0:29:28.34.Default.Geto.0.0.0..We won't have to feel bad sending you off.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:28.34.0:29:30.59.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I talk normally at school!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:33.26.0:29:34.14.Default.Riko.0.0.0..School!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:34.14.0:29:35.60.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Kuroi. what time is it?!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:35.60.0:29:38.72.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..It's not yet noon. But I think going to school—
Dialogue: 0.0:29:38.72.0:29:39.56.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:39.56.0:29:41.35.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I said I'm going. and I'm going!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:43.56.0:29:44.81.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Huh?!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:45.63.0:29:48.70.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Surely it'd be safer to head \Nback to Jujutsu High at once!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:49.03.0:29:53.78.Italics.Yaga.0.0.0..As much as I want to do that. \Nthis is an order from Tengen-sama.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:54.11.0:29:57.62.Italics.Yaga.0.0.0..He said to fulfill all of \NAmanai Riko's demands.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:59.04.0:30:00.16.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Tsk.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:03.67.0:30:05.83.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Lax upbringing at its finest.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:06.36.0:30:08.05.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Don't be like that. Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:08.05.0:30:09.38.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Despite what she may say.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:09.38.0:30:11.67.Default.Geto.0.0.0..after the assimilation. she'll spend \Nher whole life as Tengen-sama
Dialogue: 0.0:30:11.67.0:30:14.18.Default.Geto.0.0.0..in the deepest floor of Jujutsu High. \Nas the foundation of all barriers.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:14.72.0:30:19.77.Default.Geto.0.0.0..She won't be able to see her friends. \Nfamily. or anyone precious to her ever again.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:20.89.0:30:22.27.Default.Classmate.0.0.0..Riko!
Dialogue: 0.0:30:23.60.0:30:25.12.Default.Classmate.0.0.0..Our next class is in a different room.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:25.12.0:30:25.68.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Okay!
Dialogue: 0.0:30:26.06.0:30:27.52.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Let her do what she wants.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:28.23.0:30:30.99.Default.Geto.0.0.0..That's part of our mission.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:33.87.0:30:36.49.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Riko-sama has no family.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:36.49.0:30:38.47.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..They were in an accident when she was little.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:38.47.0:30:41.29.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..I've taken care of her ever since then.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:41.95.0:30:45.34.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..So I want her to at least have \Nwhat time she can with her friends.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:46.46.0:30:49.00.Default.Geto.0.0.0..So you're her family. then.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:51.59.0:30:52.50.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:55.80.0:30:57.01.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Suguru.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:57.01.0:30:58.93.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..How're the cursed spirits you \Nsent to watch over her?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:00.10.0:31:03.98.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I just wish I could share my senses \Nwith them like Mei-san does.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:03.98.0:31:06.85.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Even so. they'll let us know as \Nsoon as anything unusual happens.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:07.94.0:31:09.11.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:09.11.0:31:11.07.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Hurry to Riko-chan's side.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:11.07.0:31:11.98.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:13.60.0:31:15.52.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Two have been exorcised.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:16.02.0:31:18.32.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Who will be the ace of the next generation?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:18.32.0:31:20.99.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}This will be an important match \Nto help us find out.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:21.58.0:31:24.54.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Number 6's final position \Nis finally starting to solidify.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:24.54.0:31:28.08.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Now. the fifth race. the one all eyes \Nare focused on. is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:31.16.0:31:32.66.Default.Laptop.0.0.0..AMANAI RIKO\NRENCHOKU GIRLS' ACADEMY\NDEAD OR ALIVE
Dialogue: 0.0:31:42.47.0:31:43.89.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Where's Amanai?!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:43.89.0:31:45.93.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..She has music this period.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:45.93.0:31:48.02.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..so either the music room or the chapel.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:48.02.0:31:49.65.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Chapel?!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:49.65.0:31:52.07.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..It changes depending on what \Nthe music teacher wants.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:52.07.0:31:53.94.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Also. this is a missionary school.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:54.28.0:31:55.86.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru. you take the chapel.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:55.86.0:31:57.49.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Kuroi-san. take the music room.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:57.49.0:31:59.36.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'll take the two unknowns.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:59.36.0:32:00.90.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Roger that.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:01.37.0:32:02.83.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I told you not to follow me!
Dialogue: 0.0:32:02.83.0:32:05.37.Default.Riko.0.0.0..What if my friends see you?!
Dialogue: 0.0:32:05.37.0:32:07.00.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:07.00.0:32:09.83.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..I even told her to text us \Nwhen she was on the move.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:09.83.0:32:13.92.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..This is why I told that brat to stay within \Neyeshot so we could protect her!
Dialogue: 0.0:32:16.92.0:32:18.05.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}And they're off.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:18.05.0:32:20.51.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Numbers 1 and 2 make a good start. \Nfavoring the inside.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:20.51.0:32:22.60.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Number 3 trails a bit behind.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:21.09.0:32:22.68.Default.Touji.0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:22.60.0:32:25.97.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Taking the lead at the first mark of \Nthe first lap is Number 2. Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:22.97.0:32:25.14.Default.Touji.0.0.0..They didn't go back to Jujutsu High?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:25.14.0:32:26.68.Default.Touji.0.0.0..Lucky me.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:25.97.0:32:27.41.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Behind him is Number 1. Masaki.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:27.41.0:32:29.60.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}They're followed by Number 3. Kawano.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:27.66.0:32:31.73.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Now the ones drawn to the bounty will\N be reasonable fools instead of just fools.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:29.60.0:32:34.40.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Then comes Number 4. Nomiya. Number 5. \NMifune. and in last is Number 6. Funegi.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:31.73.0:32:33.07.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:33.07.0:32:34.40.Default.Toji.0.0.0..About what?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:34.73.0:32:39.26.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..The bounty is the thirty-million deposit \Nthat the Star Religious Group paid you.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:39.66.0:32:42.78.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..If they kill the Star Plasma Vessel. \Nthe deposit is gone.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:42.78.0:32:45.54.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..and worst-case. you might not \Nget the full reward. either.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:45.54.0:32:48.25.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..They might start saying \Nthey could have posted
Dialogue: 0.0:32:48.25.0:32:50.75.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..a bounty from the start \Ninstead of hiring you.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:50.75.0:32:53.73.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Gojo Satoru is with the girl.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:53.73.0:32:56.09.Default.Toji.0.0.0..He's the first in several \Ncenturies to possess both
Dialogue: 0.0:32:56.09.0:32:58.17.Default.Toji.0.0.0..the Six Eyes and the Limitless technique.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:58.17.0:33:02.34.Default.Toji.0.0.0..No one can kill the Star Plasma \NVessel as long as he's nearby.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:02.34.0:33:03.86.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..Not even you?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:12.65.0:33:14.79.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Number 3. Kawano. \Nis making a rushing comeback!
Dialogue: 0.0:33:14.79.0:33:16.65.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}He's pulled into first place!
Dialogue: 0.0:33:16.65.0:33:19.26.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Who knows?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:19.49.0:33:22.03.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}He's managed to take the lead twice now.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:20.82.0:33:25.45.Default.Toji.0.0.0..For now. we'll leave the bounty\N up for another 47 hours.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:22.03.0:33:25.45.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}This race has been \Nfilled with ups and downs.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:25.45.0:33:27.54.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}Can Number 3. Kawano. \Ndefend his position at the top?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:25.78.0:33:30.21.Default.Toji.0.0.0..and let the fools wear down Gojo \Nand the sorcerers with him.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:27.54.0:33:29.71.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}The race is now entering its third lap.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:38.71.0:33:39.80.Default.Oldman.0.0.0..Hey!
Dialogue: 0.0:33:40.17.0:33:41.47.Default.Oldman.0.0.0..Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0.0:33:47.81.0:33:49.44.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Nah. never mind.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:52.69.0:33:54.98.Default.Toji.0.0.0..They won't be able to kill the \NStar Plasma Vessel. of course.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:54.98.0:33:56.48.Default.Toji.0.0.0..so they're working for free.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:56.98.0:33:59.90.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..{\i1}It's a good thing you put \Nthat time limit on it.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:59.90.0:34:02.70.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..{\i1}The curse users are \Nquickly flocking to them.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:02.70.0:34:04.66.Default.Toji.0.0.0..That's not the only reason.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:04.66.0:34:05.28.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..{\i1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:06.62.0:34:07.95.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:07.95.0:34:09.16.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:09.95.0:34:13.63.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Number 3. Kawano. just lost his balance. \Nand Number 2. Yamazaki. is passing him!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:13.87.0:34:15.83.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Number 3 has drifted far to the outside.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:13.92.0:34:15.83.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I'll head out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:15.83.0:34:18.05.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Looks like things are developing \Nfaster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:15.83.0:34:18.21.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}but he's righted his boat \Nand is chasing after them!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:18.21.0:34:20.21.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8}But there is now a considerable \Ngap between them!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:18.55.0:34:21.51.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Make sure you get that \Nthirty million back for me.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:21.51.0:34:23.72.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Number 2. Yamazaki. crosses the goal first!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:23.72.0:34:25.43.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Number 5. Mifune. crosses next.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:24.09.0:34:25.43.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..{\i1}Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:25.43.0:34:27.97.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..{\i1}This wasn't your average \Nanonymous message board.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:25.43.0:34:27.97.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Number 1. Masaki. crosses next. \Nfollowed by Number 3. Kawano.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:27.97.0:34:30.65.Italics.Announcer.0.0.0..{\an8\i1}Following them is Number 4. Nomiya. \Nand last is Number 6. Funegi.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:27.97.0:34:30.65.Italics.Kong.0.0.0..{\i1}- There are posting fees. handling fees. and—
Dialogue: 0.0:34:29.01.0:34:30.65.Default.Toji.0.0.0..- Signal's dropping.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:30.97.0:34:32.10.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Hey!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:33.39.0:34:35.06.Default.Kong.0.0.0..That bastard.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:45.06.0:34:47.29.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Are the unknowns remnants of Q?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:47.65.0:34:51.20.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..This will be a little troublesome if they've \Nbeen sent by the Star Religious Group.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:53.84.0:34:56.33.Default.Elder.0.0.0..That uniform...
Dialogue: 0.0:35:01.42.0:35:04.88.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..As soon as he saw the Jujutsu High \Nuniform. he anticipated a fight against
Dialogue: 0.0:35:04.88.0:35:07.47.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..multiple opponents and set \Nshikigami in front of and behind him.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:07.47.0:35:08.93.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..He's experienced.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:10.56.0:35:12.22.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..No catalyst?!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:12.22.0:35:14.64.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..Their cursed energy is different \Nfrom the sorcerer's. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:14.64.0:35:15.98.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0.0:35:15.98.0:35:17.73.Default.Elder.0.0.0..Curse Manipulation?!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:18.09.0:35:19.31.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Correct.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:19.31.0:35:22.11.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Living a long life has its perks. I see.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:22.11.0:35:25.28.Default.Elder.0.0.0..Nah. it's not worth \Nliving too long. you know.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:25.28.0:35:28.57.Default.Elder.0.0.0..It costs money just to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:28.57.0:35:31.33.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..His cursed technique is stronger than mine.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:31.33.0:35:34.79.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..However. he thinks like \Na typical shikigami user.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:34.79.0:35:37.08.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..Add his youth on top of that.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:37.08.0:35:40.54.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..and I can tell exactly what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:40.54.0:35:42.30.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..I knew it.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:42.30.0:35:45.09.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..Types like him never \Nstep forward themselves.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:45.34.0:35:47.97.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..Close combat is his weakness!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:47.97.0:35:53.52.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..Plus. he thinks a shikigami user \Nlike me would never get close to him.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:53.52.0:35:57.10.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..He's someone who hates close \Ncombat. and he isn't wary of it.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:57.10.0:35:59.98.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..No one is easier to kill.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:00.31.0:36:03.44.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Looks like you're thinking up lots of plans.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:03.69.0:36:05.03.Default.Geto.0.0.0..but there's no point.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:10.37.0:36:10.87.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..What?!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:10.87.0:36:13.62.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..Those first two were to prevent \Nme from anticipating this?!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:18.42.0:36:21.13.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Now. that leaves one more.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:25.13.0:36:26.76.Default.Elder.0.0.0..You're mine!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:43.00.0:36:46.49.Default.Elder.0.0.0..Tasuke? Is that you. Tasuke?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:47.22.0:36:51.66.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..My parents used all their time and money \Non my well-behaved little brother.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:51.66.0:36:55.37.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..They thought I was creepy \Nbecause I could see the unseen.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:55.91.0:37:01.00.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..But Tasuke was my one and only friend. \Nwho interacted with me without such fear.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:03.17.0:37:05.34.Default.Elder.0.0.0..It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:05.34.0:37:08.22.Default.Elder.0.0.0..Has it been over 50 years already?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:08.22.0:37:11.01.Default.Elder.0.0.0..Since the day you died—
Dialogue: 0.0:37:11.72.0:37:13.30.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..I see now!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:19.02.0:37:20.94.Italics.Elder.0.0.0..My life flashed before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:21.35.0:37:23.61.Default.Elder.0.0.0..You lured me in!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:23.61.0:37:24.86.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Well. yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:24.86.0:37:28.13.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You were itching to get in \Nclose that whole time. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:28.13.0:37:30.07.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Those with a set means of victory
Dialogue: 0.0:37:30.07.0:37:33.11.Default.Geto.0.0.0..will easily jump on the chance \Nwhen you give them that opening.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:34.87.0:37:38.10.Default.Geto.0.0.0..More importantly. are you with Q?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:38.10.0:37:39.58.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Or the Star Religious Group?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:03.02.0:38:04.23.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Amanai!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:09.82.0:38:12.40.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wha...
Dialogue: 0.0:38:12.40.0:38:13.99.Default.Girls.0.0.0..What?!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:13.99.0:38:15.74.Default.GirlD.0.0.0..Riko. you have a boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:15.74.0:38:18.62.Default.Riko.0.0.0..No! He's a cousin! Just a cousin!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:18.62.0:38:20.25.Default.GirlC.0.0.0..You're a smooth operator.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:20.25.0:38:22.08.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I told you. he's not!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:22.08.0:38:24.42.Default.GirlA.0.0.0..A high schooler?! He's so tall!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:24.42.0:38:25.92.Default.GirlA.0.0.0..Hey. mister!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:25.92.0:38:27.42.Default.GirlF.0.0.0..Take off your sunglasses!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:30.13.0:38:31.94.Default.Girls.0.0.0..Squee! He's so hot!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:31.94.0:38:33.34.Default.GirlA.0.0.0..Such long lashes!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:32.47.0:38:33.34.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:33.34.0:38:34.97.Default.GirlB.0.0.0..Why are your eyes blue?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:34.97.0:38:37.18.Default.Girl.0.0.0..Could you pose for me?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:37.72.0:38:39.64.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Hey! Quit getting carried away!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:39.64.0:38:41.85.Default.Teacher.0.0.0..All right. everyone! Quiet down!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:41.85.0:38:43.60.Default.Teacher.0.0.0..This is disgraceful!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:43.60.0:38:45.98.Default.GirlA.0.0.0..You know you're curious \Nabout him. too. Sensei!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:45.98.0:38:47.31.Default.GirlB.0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:47.66.0:38:49.11.Default.Teacher.0.0.0..This is inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:49.11.0:38:51.40.Default.Teacher.0.0.0..Even if you are a relative. \Nyou can't just barge in.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:51.40.0:38:55.36.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Oh. you'll have to forgive me.\NIt was an emergency.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:57.82.0:38:59.53.Default.Teacher.0.0.0..Also. here. My phone number.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:59.53.0:39:01.79.Default.Girls.0.0.0..Hey! That's against the rules!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:00.14.0:39:00.89.Default.Girls.0.0.0..{\fad(167.167)\an8\bord3\shad0\fnArial\b1\c&HBEFBFA&\3c&H725933&}GRAAAH
Dialogue: 0.0:39:01.79.0:39:04.59.Default.Teacher.0.0.0..Shut up! You don't get many chances \Nto meet people as a teacher!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:04.59.0:39:06.79.Default.GirlA.0.0.0..The same is true for us. too!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:06.79.0:39:09.21.Default.GirlB.0.0.0..I can't believe you're into younger men! \NI've lost respect for you!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:09.21.0:39:11.76.Default.Teacher.0.0.0..What?! You dissin' Hikaru Genji?!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:11.76.0:39:13.69.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..What a lively school.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:13.69.0:39:16.98.Default.Riko.0.0.0..You idiot! I told you not to show \Nyourself before my friends!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:17.64.0:39:20.43.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Curse users attacked. Figure out the rest.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:21.85.0:39:23.10.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I'm floating?!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:28.47.0:39:30.16.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..We're heading to Jujutsu High now.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:30.60.0:39:32.93.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You don't want you friends to \Nget caught up in this. do you?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:35.24.0:39:37.24.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Is that the thirty million?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:37.24.0:39:39.20.Default.Bag.0.0.0..The one with her is another sorcerer?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:39.20.0:39:41.01.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Her bodyguard. too. I bet.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:41.34.0:39:42.87.Default.Bag.0.0.0..What a sweet deal.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:42.87.0:39:45.71.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Thirty million for killing a kid \Nwho's not even a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:45.71.0:39:47.50.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Maybe I'll have eel tonight?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:47.50.0:39:49.71.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Food always tastes best \Nafter killing someone.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:49.71.0:39:52.17.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Are you from the Star Religious Group?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:52.55.0:39:56.82.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..The people in Q wore even weirder outfits.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:57.05.0:39:58.55.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Are you a rookie?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:58.55.0:40:00.68.Default.Bag.0.0.0..If you're killing someone. do it without talking.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:04.85.0:40:06.02.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Too slow.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:19.43.0:40:21.62.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Don't you dare take anything from that girl.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:22.35.0:40:23.83.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:28.96.0:40:30.13.Default.Geto.0.0.0..What's this?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:31.04.0:40:32.71.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Well. aren't you strong?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:33.97.0:40:35.13.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Where's Riko-chan?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:35.92.0:40:38.51.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..She left the school with Gojo-sama.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:38.51.0:40:41.18.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Then we should head that way. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:41.18.0:40:43.59.Default.Geto.0.0.0..This has gotten a bit troublesome.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:44.85.0:40:47.64.Default.Bag.0.0.0..So that really was the thirty million earlier.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:50.65.0:40:52.06.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..A shikigami?!
Dialogue: 0.0:40:52.06.0:40:54.52.Default.Geto.0.0.0..No. it's not quite the same as a shikigami.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:54.90.0:40:55.94.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:56.32.0:40:59.15.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..There's a bounty of thirty \Nmillion on Amanai's head?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:59.15.0:41:03.12.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Yeah. It was posted on an \Nunderground site for curse users.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:03.12.0:41:05.83.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Apparently. the time limit is\N11 AM the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:06.33.0:41:07.83.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Now things make sense.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:08.80.0:41:12.58.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Two. three. four... They all look the same.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:12.58.0:41:13.88.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Are they shikigami?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:14.23.0:41:18.55.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Jeez... And jujutsu sorcerers are \Nshort-handed all year round.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:18.55.0:41:21.57.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..If you want to change jobs. \Nwe'll welcome you. old man.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:21.57.0:41:24.89.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Nah. public employment \Nain't easy work. either.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:24.89.0:41:27.52.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Just hand over that brat and we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:27.52.0:41:29.07.Default.Riko.0.0.0..There's more! Five of them now!
Dialogue: 0.0:41:29.07.0:41:32.35.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..What's so great about this brat?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:41.36.0:41:43.09.Default.Bag.0.0.0..What did you just do?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:43.35.0:41:44.91.Default.Riko.0.0.0..The shikigami isn't disappearing!
Dialogue: 0.0:41:44.91.0:41:46.62.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Which is the real one?!
Dialogue: 0.0:41:46.62.0:41:47.89.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..They're not shikigami.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:47.89.0:41:49.20.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..They're clones.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:49.20.0:41:51.46.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..And each one is the real one.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:56.13.0:41:57.67.Default.Bag.0.0.0..The hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0.0:41:57.67.0:41:58.59.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Infinity.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:58.59.0:42:00.30.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..It's Achilles and the Tortoise.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:00.30.0:42:01.13.Default.Bag.0.0.0..Huh?!
Dialogue: 0.0:42:01.13.0:42:03.64.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..It's important to study. you know.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:05.72.0:42:09.14.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Yours is a cloning technique that allows \Na maximum of five. including the original.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:09.14.0:42:13.02.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..And you're always free to decide which \Nof the clones is the main body. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:42:13.02.0:42:15.23.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So if your main body is in danger.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:15.23.0:42:17.69.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..you make a safe clone the main body.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:17.69.0:42:19.65.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..That's a nice technique you have there.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:19.65.0:42:22.57.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I don't understand why you're so weak.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:23.53.0:42:27.05.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Are you unable to produce a clone \Nfor a while after it's destroyed?
Dialogue: 0.0:42:27.05.0:42:29.54.Default.Bag.0.0.0..How do you know what my technique is?
Dialogue: 0.0:42:29.54.0:42:31.12.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Unfortunately for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:31.12.0:42:32.87.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I have good eyes.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:33.52.0:42:35.54.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You see. my technique
Dialogue: 0.0:42:35.54.0:42:38.63.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..is like a convergent \Nseries of infinite numbers.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:38.63.0:42:41.49.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Anything that approaches me \Ngrows slower and slower.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:41.49.0:42:44.47.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..and ultimately. it fails to ever reach me.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:45.00.0:42:47.51.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..When I amplify my Limitless technique.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:47.51.0:42:50.27.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I get what you might call \Na negative natural number.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:50.27.0:42:53.85.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..It basically creates a \Nsingle imaginary apple.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:54.48.0:42:57.48.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Doing so causes everything around to \Nget sucked into that space. like you saw.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:57.77.0:42:59.48.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Though it's surprisingly inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:59.73.0:43:03.65.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I can't create too large \Na reaction near myself.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:03.65.0:43:05.95.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..and if I start worrying \Nabout the vectors. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:05.95.0:43:08.91.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..controlling the cursed \Nenergy becomes a real pain.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:09.26.0:43:11.68.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Basically. it's super exhausting.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:15.12.0:43:19.13.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..But that's all just the proper \Noperation of the technique.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:20.92.0:43:22.80.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Protect your head.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:39.56.0:43:41.86.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..This next one is the divergence of infinity.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:44.15.0:43:45.96.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..My reverse cursed technique.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:47.57.0:43:48.45.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Red!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:03.76.0:44:05.26.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I failed!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:15.18.0:44:18.14.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I really thought I could do it that time.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:18.98.0:44:21.15.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..Is this guy for real?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:24.07.0:44:25.49.Default.Riko.0.0.0..It's from Kuroi.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:29.52.0:44:31.02.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Wh-What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:31.52.0:44:32.61.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Kuroi has...
Dialogue: 0.0:44:33.28.0:44:34.53.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Kuroi has been...
Dialogue: 0.0:44:37.22.0:44:39.39.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..There's always a chance \Nthe worst could happen.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:39.70.0:44:41.52.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..You're much faster than me.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:41.52.0:44:43.52.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..so go on ahead! Hurry to Riko's side!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:46.69.0:44:49.32.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'm sorry. This was my mistake.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:49.32.0:44:50.58.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Really?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:50.58.0:44:52.98.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I don't think this even counts as a mistake.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:52.98.0:44:56.57.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I underestimated how much our \Nenemies would value Kuroi-san.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:57.01.0:44:58.36.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Their next move
Dialogue: 0.0:44:58.36.0:45:01.08.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..will probably be offering to \Narrange an exchange for her.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:01.08.0:45:03.80.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Something like trading Amanai for Kuroi-san.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:03.80.0:45:06.93.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..or saying they'll kill Kuroi-san \Nif we don't kill Amanai.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:07.89.0:45:11.51.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..But we have the leverage in any \Nnegotiations since we have Amanai.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:12.08.0:45:14.42.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..As long as they set up \Nthe location for the deal.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:14.42.0:45:16.58.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..we can make it work out.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:17.22.0:45:19.94.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I'm taking Amanai back to Jujutsu High now.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:19.94.0:45:23.03.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..We can have Shoko or someone \Nstand in as her body double.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:22.01.0:45:23.03.Default.Riko.0.0.0..{\an8}H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:24.05.0:45:26.14.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I'm going to this deal. too!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:26.14.0:45:27.97.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I still can't trust you two yet!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:27.97.0:45:30.69.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Huh?! You're still saying \Nthat after all this. you—
Dialogue: 0.0:45:30.69.0:45:32.35.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Even if you do manage to save her...
Dialogue: 0.0:45:33.54.0:45:37.59.Default.Riko.0.0.0..What if Kuroi isn't back before \NI assimilate with Tengen-sama?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:38.85.0:45:39.57.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I haven't...
Dialogue: 0.0:45:43.22.0:45:45.01.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I haven't even said goodbye to her!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:56.31.0:45:59.04.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The kidnapper will reach \Nout to us eventually.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:59.80.0:46:02.76.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..If they seem like they're \Nsmarter than we expect.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:02.76.0:46:07.35.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..and bringing you with us is likely to \Nhurt Kuroi-san's chance of survival...
Dialogue: 0.0:46:11.10.0:46:13.29.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..then we will leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:21.28.0:46:24.03.Default.Riko.0.0.0..All right. That works.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:25.04.0:46:26.84.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..In exchange.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:26.84.0:46:30.49.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..if you get scared partway through and \Nwant to go home. we'll just ignore you.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:31.46.0:46:32.88.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Bear that in mind.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:38.36.0:46:41.25.Default.Both.0.0.0..Mensore!
Dialogue: 0.0:46:48.02.0:46:51.02.Default.Screen.0.0.0..OKINAWA
Dialogue: 0.0:46:51.02.0:46:52.79.Default..0.0.0..PROTECTION MISSION DAY 2
Dialogue: 0.0:46:57.79.0:47:00.23.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..I can't believe I got captured \Nby the Star Religious Group.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:00.23.0:47:02.26.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..and by a non-sorcerer at that.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:02.59.0:47:04.75.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..I'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:04.75.0:47:07.38.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You couldn't help it if they \Ncaught you off-guard.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:07.38.0:47:09.26.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Part of the blame lies with me. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:09.79.0:47:13.01.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Was I really caught off-guard?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:14.50.0:47:18.61.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..I thought I was on high alert \Nafter the incident with Q.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:19.45.0:47:20.91.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Kuroi!
Dialogue: 0.0:47:22.63.0:47:26.11.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..I still don't have much \Nrecollection of being attacked.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:26.40.0:47:29.18.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..And you all came here by plane?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:29.18.0:47:30.74.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Were you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:30.74.0:47:32.24.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..You weren't attacked?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:32.57.0:47:34.33.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru has good eyes.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:35.93.0:47:38.75.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Before we took off. he checked over \Nall the passengers and staff.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:39.97.0:47:42.40.Default.Geto.0.0.0..as well as the inside \Nand outside of the plane.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:43.16.0:47:46.92.Default.Geto.0.0.0..And while we were in the air. I had \Nmy cursed spirit keep watch outside.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:48.86.0:47:51.45.Default.Geto.0.0.0..It was safer than using a land route.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:52.69.0:47:54.67.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'm more curious as to why
Dialogue: 0.0:47:54.67.0:47:57.94.Default.Geto.0.0.0..they designated Okinawa for the exchange.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:58.27.0:48:00.44.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Probably to buy time. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:00.44.0:48:05.44.Default - Copy.ScreenTop.0.0.0..TRAVEL SCHEDULE
Dialogue: 0.0:48:05.47.0:48:10.87.Default - Copy.ScreenRight.0.0.0..ASSIMILATE WITH TENGEN-SAMA\NAFTER SUNSET!\NPROTECTION MISSION FINISHED
Dialogue: 1.0:48:00.99.0:48:02.90.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Even if they fail to kill Riko-sama.
Dialogue: 1.0:48:02.90.0:48:05.47.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..they could keep her from making \Ntomorrow's full moon deadline.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:05.47.0:48:07.00.Default.Geto.0.0.0..If that were the goal.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:07.00.0:48:10.41.Default.Geto.0.0.0..they would choose a rural area \Nwith poor transit infrastructure.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:10.41.0:48:13.88.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..You don't think they're planning \Nto take over the airport. do you?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:13.88.0:48:15.22.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:15.22.0:48:16.41.Default.Geto.0.0.0..But we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 1.0:48:16.79.0:48:19.90.Default.Geto.0.0.0..We're not the only ones who came here.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:21.91.0:48:26.09.Default.Nanami.0.0.0..Clearly this isn't a mission \Nfit for a first-year.
Dialogue: 1.0:48:23.13.0:48:26.09.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..JUJUTSU HIGH\NFIRST YEAR\NNANAMI KENTO
Dialogue: 0.0:48:26.09.0:48:28.31.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..I'm psyched. though!
Dialogue: 1.0:48:26.09.0:48:30.93.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..JUJUTSU HIGH\NFIRST YEAR\NHAIBARA YU
Dialogue: 0.0:48:28.31.0:48:30.93.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..I want to show off in front of Geto-san. too!
Dialogue: 0.0:48:30.93.0:48:34.54.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Besides. I hear our upperclassmen \Nare wearing themselves to the bone
Dialogue: 0.0:48:34.54.0:48:36.45.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..to protect an innocent young girl!
Dialogue: 0.0:48:36.45.0:48:39.40.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..So we have to give it our all. too!
Dialogue: 0.0:48:39.80.0:48:43.73.Default.Nanami.0.0.0..If a typhoon rolls in and shuts down the \Nairports. our efforts will be for naught.
Dialogue: 1.0:48:45.15.0:48:47.65.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..UPPERCLASSMAN WEARING HIMSELF TO THE BONE
Dialogue: 0.0:48:46.17.0:48:47.65.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Sea cucumber. sea cucumber!
Dialogue: 0.0:48:47.65.0:48:50.62.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Gross! That's so gross!
Dialogue: 0.0:48:51.73.0:48:53.99.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Should we really be sightseeing like this?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:53.99.0:48:56.26.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru's the one who suggested it.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:56.96.0:49:00.14.Default.Geto.0.0.0..He's probably showing consideration \Nfor Riko-chan. in his own way.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:01.09.0:49:02.54.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Though it is getting close...
Dialogue: 0.0:49:03.07.0:49:05.62.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru! It's time.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:05.62.0:49:07.44.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Oh. it's that time already?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:09.46.0:49:11.05.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Boo.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:13.05.0:49:16.30.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Suguru. let's head back \Ntomorrow morning instead.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:18.53.0:49:19.94.Default.Geto.0.0.0..But...
Dialogue: 0.0:49:19.94.0:49:22.19.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The weather's holding steady. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:23.43.0:49:24.32.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Besides...
Dialogue: 0.0:49:24.81.0:49:29.22.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..there are fewer curse users in \NOkinawa than there are in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:27.07.0:49:31.61.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..CURSE USERS
Dialogue: 0.0:49:29.22.0:49:31.62.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Let's keep it a little more serious. Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:32.42.0:49:36.22.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..It's better if the time limit on the bounty \Nruns out while we're mid-flight. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:33.18.0:49:35.10.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..{\an8}Young lady. a starfish.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:35.75.0:49:36.95.Default.Riko.0.0.0..{\an8}So it is!
Dialogue: 0.0:49:36.95.0:49:38.12.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:38.12.0:49:41.11.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You haven't released your technique \Nsince yesterday. have you?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:41.39.0:49:42.69.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You haven't slept. either.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:42.69.0:49:44.63.Default.Geto.0.0.0..And you don't plan to sleep tonight. do you?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:45.08.0:49:48.01.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Are you sure we don't need \Nto go back to Jujutsu High?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:50.13.0:49:52.07.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..It's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:52.07.0:49:55.80.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Playing through 99 years of {\i1}MomoTetsu{\i0} \Nwas far more draining.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:57.39.0:50:00.14.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Besides. you're here. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:06.62.0:50:09.60.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Nanami. they said they're \Nextending their stay another day!
Dialogue: 0.0:50:09.60.0:50:11.19.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..You think something happened?!
Dialogue: 0.0:51:58.01.0:52:00.26.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..TOKYO JUJUTSU HIGH. FOOTHILLS OF MT. MUSHIRO
Dialogue: 0.0:52:01.76.0:52:06.52.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..PROTECTION MISSION DAY 3 15:00
Dialogue: 0.0:52:04.57.0:52:06.52.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Good work. everyone.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:09.02.0:52:11.10.Default.Geto.0.0.0..We're inside Jujutsu High's barrier now.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:12.53.0:52:14.55.Default.Riko.0.0.0..What a relief.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:14.55.0:52:15.57.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:17.60.0:52:18.62.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:20.44.0:52:22.33.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You really worked hard this time.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:25.73.0:52:28.91.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I never wanna get stuck \Nbabysitting a brat again.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:28.91.0:52:29.76.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:38.82.0:52:39.87.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Impossible!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:40.38.0:52:44.56.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..We're inside Jujutsu High's barrier!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:44.92.0:52:48.30.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:48.30.0:52:49.65.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:49.65.0:52:54.32.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I'm terrible at remembering guys' names. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:58.07.0:53:03.53.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..I once went to see the brat born into \Nthe Gojo clan with the Six Eyes on a lark.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:23.40.0:53:25.18.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..Never before or after that
Dialogue: 0.0:53:25.18.0:53:29.44.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..had anyone noticed me standing behind them.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:30.32.0:53:32.58.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..That is why I wore him down...
Dialogue: 0.0:53:37.40.0:53:39.37.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..until his senses dulled.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:49.54.0:53:50.58.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru!
Dialogue: 0.0:53:52.05.0:53:53.81.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:53.81.0:53:57.01.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I didn't make it in time with my\Ntechnique. but it missed my vitals.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:57.40.0:53:59.42.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I then strengthened myself \Nwith cursed energy
Dialogue: 0.0:53:59.42.0:54:01.57.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..so the blade couldn't be drawn out at all.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:02.21.0:54:06.24.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..It was like passing a safety \Npin through a knit sweater.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:06.74.0:54:08.40.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Seriously. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:08.72.0:54:11.15.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Prioritize Amanai first.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:11.46.0:54:13.59.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I'll deal with this guy.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:14.36.0:54:18.18.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Suguru. you two get her to Tengen-sama.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:19.45.0:54:20.64.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru...
Dialogue: 0.0:54:26.43.0:54:27.83.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Be careful!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:28.29.0:54:29.16.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Let's go!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:29.68.0:54:30.30.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Right!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:31.38.0:54:33.30.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:40.53.0:54:43.69.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..That's different from the \Nblade he stabbed me with.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:44.02.0:54:46.56.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..And where did that \Ncursed spirit come from?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:47.02.0:54:49.56.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Too many unknowns. damn it!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:50.04.0:54:52.16.Default.Toji.0.0.0..The Star Plasma Vessel is gone.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:52.83.0:54:55.86.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I had hoped to take you down \Nwith that earlier attack.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:55.86.0:54:57.06.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I guess I've gotten rusty.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:57.31.0:55:00.58.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The bounty on Amanai has already \Nbeen taken down. you idiot.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:00.84.0:55:03.57.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Because I took it down. prideful bastard.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:04.10.0:55:06.46.Default.Toji.0.0.0..When facing people \Nwithout openings like you.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:06.46.0:55:09.96.Default.Toji.0.0.0..you have to first create ups and \Ndowns leading to several false goals.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:10.33.0:55:14.57.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I laughed when those Star Religious \NGroup men went to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:14.87.0:55:18.50.Default.Toji.0.0.0..It sucked that none of the \Nsorcerers around her died.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:18.50.0:55:20.97.Default.Toji.0.0.0..but if I hadn't set that \Ntime limit on the bounty.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:21.78.0:55:25.47.Default.Toji.0.0.0..you wouldn't have released \Nyour technique until the very end.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:26.06.0:55:27.53.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..That so?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:33.14.0:55:34.36.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..He's fast!
Dialogue: 0.0:55:34.84.0:55:36.18.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..And not just that.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:36.18.0:55:39.21.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..I knew there was something off about him!
Dialogue: 0.0:55:39.21.0:55:41.21.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..He has zero cursed energy!
Dialogue: 0.0:55:41.80.0:55:44.83.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..He has a Heavenly Pact \Ngifting him physical prowess!
Dialogue: 0.0:56:17.11.0:56:20.62.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..I can't imagine anyone who knows \Nmy technique coming without a plan.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:21.16.0:56:23.12.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Is that cursed tool your \Nprecious trump card?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:23.12.0:56:25.84.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Sorry. but I won't let it get close!
Dialogue: 0.0:56:40.90.0:56:43.54.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Since he has no cursed energy. \NI can't read his presence.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:43.54.0:56:46.68.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..And I can't just rely on instinct.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:46.68.0:56:49.47.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..There's that cursed spirit \Nwrapped around him.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:49.47.0:56:52.06.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..I just need to follow its presence.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:53.62.0:56:57.45.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Even so. he's too damn fast!
Dialogue: 0.0:56:57.94.0:56:59.70.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Cursed Technique Amplification.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:00.31.0:57:01.86.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Maximum Output...
Dialogue: 0.0:57:07.81.0:57:08.53.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Blue!
Dialogue: 0.0:57:23.63.0:57:25.38.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Now there's no cover.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:25.38.0:57:27.05.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..He can't launch surprise attacks.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:27.05.0:57:28.69.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Did he hide in the woods?
Dialogue: 0.0:57:31.20.0:57:32.18.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Are those...
Dialogue: 0.0:57:33.30.0:57:34.68.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Fly Heads?!
Dialogue: 0.0:57:39.08.0:57:41.82.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Was he keeping them inside \Nthat cursed spirit?
Dialogue: 0.0:57:42.10.0:57:44.58.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So you're using Fly Heads like chaff.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:45.02.0:57:47.50.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Now I can't tell where he is.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:48.31.0:57:50.34.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..He's created a blind spot.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:50.34.0:57:51.78.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..I should use Blue again...
Dialogue: 0.0:57:52.44.0:57:55.33.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..No. wait! He's after...
Dialogue: 0.0:57:55.33.0:57:56.67.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Amanai!
Dialogue: 0.0:58:03.45.0:58:05.88.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..His intuition is keen enough \Nto sense me empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:06.26.0:58:08.83.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..There's no way your Six Eyes would overlook
Dialogue: 0.0:58:09.21.0:58:12.06.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..the unusual cursed energy \Noozing from this cursed tool.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:13.42.0:58:14.79.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..Though that finally...
Dialogue: 0.0:58:17.98.0:58:20.86.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..got you to focus on defense \Nwith your technique.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:53.61.0:58:56.49.Default.Toji.0.0.0..The Special-Grade Cursed Tool. \NInverted Spear of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:56.90.0:59:00.70.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Its effect is the forced release \Nof any active techniques.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:01.79.0:59:02.60.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I think...
Dialogue: 0.0:59:06.42.0:59:08.38.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I'm getting my edge back now.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:47.16.0:59:48.13.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Riko-sama.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:49.74.0:59:51.62.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..This is as far as I go.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:53.74.0:59:55.28.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Riko-sama. please...
Dialogue: 0.0:59:55.82.0:59:56.70.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Please...
Dialogue: 0.1:00:01.19.1:00:03.91.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Kuroi. I love you!
Dialogue: 0.1:00:04.23.1:00:07.65.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I always have. and I always will!
Dialogue: 0.1:00:08.46.1:00:09.67.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..Me. too!
Dialogue: 0.1:00:10.26.1:00:12.34.Default.Kuroi.0.0.0..I love you. too!
Dialogue: 0.1:00:34.20.1:00:35.48.Default.Riko.0.0.0..So this is...
Dialogue: 0.1:00:35.48.1:00:36.49.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:36.82.1:00:38.87.Default.Geto.0.0.0..We're in Tengen-sama's territory now.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:40.46.1:00:42.62.Default.Geto.0.0.0..This is the foundation of \Nthe nation's key barriers.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:43.43.1:00:45.75.Default.Geto.0.0.0..The Main Hall of the Tombs of the Star.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:46.87.1:00:48.86.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Once you descend the stairs.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:48.86.1:00:52.88.Default.Geto.0.0.0..pass through the gate and continue \Nto the base of the big tree.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:53.27.1:00:56.53.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Then you'll be inside the special \Nbarrier that's separate from
Dialogue: 0.1:00:56.53.1:00:58.39.Default.Geto.0.0.0..the barrier surrounding Jujutsu High.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:58.87.1:01:01.57.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Only those invited are able to enter it.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:02.26.1:01:05.60.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Tengen-sama will protect \Nyou until the assimilation.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:08.23.1:01:09.64.Default.Geto.0.0.0..That...
Dialogue: 0.1:01:09.64.1:01:12.78.Default.Geto.0.0.0..or we can turn back around \Nand go home with Kuroi-san.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:17.03.1:01:17.89.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:17.89.1:01:21.50.Default.Geto.0.0.0..When our teacher told us about this mission.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:21.50.1:01:24.84.Default.Geto.0.0.0..he called the assimilation "erasing."
Dialogue: 0.1:01:25.54.1:01:29.75.Default.Geto.0.0.0..He was trying to tell us to be aware \Nof how heavy a sin that was.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:29.75.1:01:32.08.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Our teacher may be a muscle-brain.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:32.08.1:01:34.14.Default.Geto.0.0.0..but he often does roundabout things.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:38.09.1:01:42.42.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru and I already talked it \Nover before we met you.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:44.18.1:01:47.90.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..What if the Star Plasma Vessel \Nbrat refuses to assimilate?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:47.90.1:01:51.40.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Then... the assimilation's off!
Dialogue: 0.1:01:52.95.1:01:54.14.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:54.14.1:01:54.90.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:01:55.30.1:01:58.91.Default.Geto.0.0.0..It might mean fighting \NTengen-sama. you know.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:00.60.1:02:02.42.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You scared?
Dialogue: 0.1:02:02.90.1:02:05.58.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..It's fine. It'll all work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:06.49.1:02:09.18.Default.Geto.0.0.0..We are the strongest.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:09.52.1:02:12.15.Default.Geto.0.0.0..No matter what decision you make.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:12.15.1:02:14.76.Default.Geto.0.0.0..we will guarantee your future.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:19.08.1:02:20.10.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I have...
Dialogue: 0.1:02:21.13.1:02:23.27.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..always been special. \Nsince the day I was born.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:23.88.1:02:26.55.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..Everyone kept telling me \Nthat I was different.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:27.94.1:02:30.73.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..Being special was normal to me.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:31.15.1:02:33.21.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..and I've lived my life trying \Nto avoid danger
Dialogue: 0.1:02:33.21.1:02:35.32.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..as much as possible \Nfor the sake of this day.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:36.84.1:02:40.71.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..I don't really remember the \Nday my mother and father died.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:41.02.1:02:43.45.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..I no longer feel sad or lonely about that.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:45.17.1:02:46.70.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..I figured everything would be fine.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:46.70.1:02:50.17.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..even if I was taken away \Nfrom everyone and assimilated.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:53.60.1:02:55.54.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..That no matter how hard it was.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:55.93.1:02:59.72.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..it would stop feeling sad and lonely one day.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:01.48.1:03:02.46.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..But...
Dialogue: 0.1:03:03.36.1:03:04.42.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..But...
Dialogue: 0.1:03:04.92.1:03:06.20.Italics.Riko.0.0.0..Honestly...
Dialogue: 0.1:03:07.22.1:03:10.20.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I want to be with everyone longer!
Dialogue: 0.1:03:10.20.1:03:13.90.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I want to go to all kinds \Nof places with everyone!
Dialogue: 0.1:03:14.49.1:03:19.09.Default.Riko.0.0.0..I want to see all kinds \Nof things and do more!
Dialogue: 0.1:03:19.86.1:03:22.58.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Let's go home. Riko-chan.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:29.75.1:03:30.61.Default.Riko.0.0.0..Yeah!
Dialogue: 0.1:03:46.64.1:03:47.78.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Riko-chan?
Dialogue: 0.1:03:49.62.1:03:51.25.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Okay. job's done.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:53.51.1:03:55.33.Default.Toji.0.0.0..You're free to go now.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:00.24.1:04:02.50.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:04.42.1:04:05.85.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Why?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:06.37.1:04:08.90.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Oh. that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:11.26.1:04:14.42.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Because I killed Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:28.34.1:04:29.33.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Is that so?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:30.23.1:04:31.41.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Die!
Dialogue: 0.1:05:05.89.1:05:07.89.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Don't be so impatient.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:14.19.1:05:16.11.Default.Toji.0.0.0..The Tombs of the Star \Nand the Forbidden Vault
Dialogue: 0.1:05:16.11.1:05:17.70.Default.Toji.0.0.0..use barriers that conceal.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:18.03.1:05:20.20.Default.Toji.0.0.0..So they can't place guards at the entrances.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:21.28.1:05:23.58.Default.Toji.0.0.0..As long as you know where the doors are.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:23.58.1:05:25.16.Default.Toji.0.0.0..they're full of holes.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:25.62.1:05:28.41.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Sorcerers are busy during this time of year.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:28.41.1:05:31.83.Default.Toji.0.0.0..and Jujutsu High is brimming \Nwith Fly Heads right now.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:31.83.1:05:34.30.Default.Toji.0.0.0..It's pure chaos outside.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:34.69.1:05:38.22.Default.Toji.0.0.0..And since I have no cursed energy. \NI'm like the invisible man.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:38.58.1:05:41.18.Default.Toji.0.0.0..There was one problem. though.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:41.75.1:05:43.18.Default.Toji.0.0.0..If I wield a cursed tool.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:43.58.1:05:47.27.Default.Toji.0.0.0..the cursed energy from it will stop \Nme from being an invisible man.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:54.77.1:05:56.61.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Now. there's more to this story.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:58.36.1:06:01.95.Default.Toji.0.0.0..See. I keep a cursed spirit \Ncapable of storing objects around.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:01.95.1:06:04.62.Default.Toji.0.0.0..So I usually put my cursed tools \Nin it when I'm walking around.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:06.12.1:06:07.70.Default.Toji.0.0.0..You don't have to say it.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:07.70.1:06:09.41.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Yes. that means the cursed energy from
Dialogue: 0.1:06:09.41.1:06:12.25.Default.Toji.0.0.0..the cursed spirit should stop me \Nfrom being an invisible man.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:14.96.1:06:19.42.Default.Toji.0.0.0..So I make the cursed spirit smaller.\Nuntil it can fit inside my body.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:20.80.1:06:23.55.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Then I keep it inside my stomach.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:23.55.1:06:26.64.Default.Toji.0.0.0..After all. the organs of the invisible \Nman are invisible. too. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:06:26.98.1:06:29.64.Default.Toji.0.0.0..That's how I'm able to \Npass through any barrier
Dialogue: 0.1:06:29.64.1:06:32.10.Default.Toji.0.0.0..while still carrying \Nall kinds of cursed tools.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:35.77.1:06:39.94.Default.Toji.0.0.0..That's also why I didn't use \Na cursed tool at first.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:41.78.1:06:43.82.Default.Toji.0.0.0..A surprise attack on the Six Eyes
Dialogue: 0.1:06:43.82.1:06:46.41.Default.Toji.0.0.0..would be pointless if I wasn't invisible.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:46.80.1:06:50.00.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I could've killed the Star Plasma Vessel first.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:50.00.1:06:52.54.Default.Toji.0.0.0..but the risk of the Six Eyes seeing me was too—
Dialogue: 0.1:06:52.54.1:06:53.46.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Enough.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:53.46.1:06:55.25.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You have a Heavenly Pact. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:06:55.25.1:06:56.96.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I know revealing information about
Dialogue: 0.1:06:56.96.1:07:00.42.Default.Geto.0.0.0..your ability increases its fundamental \Nstrength. just like for a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:00.74.1:07:02.93.Default.Geto.0.0.0..That's not what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:04.59.1:07:07.47.Default.Geto.0.0.0..How did you know which doors \Nled to the Tombs of the Star?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:07.89.1:07:11.18.Default.Geto.0.0.0..We didn't leave even \Nthe slightest residuals.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:11.54.1:07:14.87.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Humans leave plenty of \Ntraces aside from residuals.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:14.87.1:07:17.32.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Like scents. footprints. and so on.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:17.32.1:07:19.78.Default.Toji.0.0.0..My pact enhances all five of my senses. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:20.07.1:07:22.86.Default.Geto.0.0.0..There should have been \Nanother woman on the way here.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:22.86.1:07:24.24.Default.Geto.0.0.0..What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:24.24.1:07:25.24.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Hm?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:25.66.1:07:28.08.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Oh. that maid?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:28.08.1:07:29.62.Default.Toji.0.0.0..She's probably dead.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:29.62.1:07:31.95.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I didn't care if she lived or died. though.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:31.95.1:07:33.66.Default.Toji.0.0.0..If she's lucky. she might still be alive.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:34.08.1:07:35.58.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Is that so?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:35.58.1:07:38.46.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You really should... die!
Dialogue: 0.1:08:19.48.1:08:21.90.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..That Rainbow Dragon has \Nthe toughest hide there is!
Dialogue: 0.1:08:30.14.1:08:32.10.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Curse Manipulation...
Dialogue: 0.1:08:32.97.1:08:34.23.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Riffraff.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:47.25.1:08:49.07.Default.Splitmouth.0.0.0..Hey. am...
Dialogue: 0.1:08:49.07.1:08:51.83.Default.Splitmouth.0.0.0..Am... Am I...
Dialogue: 0.1:08:51.83.1:08:53.41.Default.Splitmouth.0.0.0..pretty?
Dialogue: 0.1:08:54.65.1:08:56.25.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..A potential apparition?
Dialogue: 0.1:08:56.25.1:08:58.04.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..It deploys a simple domain that
Dialogue: 0.1:08:58.04.1:09:01.76.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..enforces non-violence on both of us \Nuntil I answer its question. then?
Dialogue: 0.1:09:02.38.1:09:04.59.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Ah. well...
Dialogue: 0.1:09:04.59.1:09:06.42.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Then I'll just come out and say
Dialogue: 0.1:09:06.42.1:09:07.69.Default.Toji.0.0.0..you're not my type.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:13.47.1:09:15.18.Default.Toji.0.0.0..So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:20.90.1:09:22.15.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Idiot.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:23.15.1:09:24.36.Default.Toji.0.0.0..It's over.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:24.94.1:09:26.11.Default.Geto.0.0.0..For you!
Dialogue: 0.1:09:29.70.1:09:31.37.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Curse Manipulation.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:31.82.1:09:33.95.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..It's a technique that lets me \Nabsorb cursed spirits
Dialogue: 0.1:09:33.95.1:09:36.37.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..that have surrendered. \Nand freely manipulate them.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:36.37.1:09:39.33.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..If there's roughly a two-grade \Ndifference in our levels.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:39.33.1:09:40.75.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..I skip making them submit
Dialogue: 0.1:09:40.75.1:09:42.92.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..and absorb them unconditionally.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:44.34.1:09:47.78.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..His cursed spirit may have a unique ability. \Nbut it's not that strong itself.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:48.34.1:09:50.93.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..I can absorb it. That'll lock down his armory.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:51.93.1:09:53.80.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Then I can just brute-force him—
Dialogue: 0.1:10:21.29.1:10:24.46.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I didn't cut you badly enough to kill you.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:24.78.1:10:27.00.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I would've killed you if \Nyou were a shikigami user.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:27.00.1:10:29.38.Default.Toji.0.0.0..but since it's Curse Manipulation.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:29.72.1:10:33.81.Default.Toji.0.0.0..there's no telling what might happen to the \Ncursed spirits you've absorbed after you die.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:35.15.1:10:37.78.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I'd rather avoid extra trouble here.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:38.31.1:10:40.02.Default.Toji.0.0.0..You have the blessing of parentage.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:40.77.1:10:43.77.Default.Toji.0.0.0..But even with that blessing.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:44.10.1:10:48.32.Default.Toji.0.0.0..you were all beaten by a monkey like me \Nwho can't even use cursed techniques.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:49.05.1:10:51.57.Default.Toji.0.0.0..If you want to live a long life. \Nnever forget that.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:55.55.1:10:58.04.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Oh. speaking of blessings...
Dialogue: 0.1:10:58.04.1:11:00.00.Default.Toji.0.0.0..That's right. I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:00.00.1:11:02.21.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I named him Megumi.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:03.47.1:11:06.23.Default - Copy.Sign.0.0.0..STAR RELIGIOUS GROUP HEADQUARTERS\NHOUSE OF THE CHILDREN OF THE STAR
Dialogue: 0.1:11:19.62.1:11:21.12.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Go on. now.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:25.68.1:11:28.67.Default.Toji.0.0.0..The corpse of the Star Plasma \NVessel. Riko Amanai.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:28.67.1:11:30.29.Default.Toji.0.0.0..All four limbs intact. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:34.58.1:11:36.34.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..Hmm. indeed.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:36.87.1:11:39.47.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..We'll issue your payment as we discussed.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:38.64.1:11:42.60.Default.Screen.0.0.0..{\fad(167.1)\p1\bord0\shad0\an5\c&HF9F9F9&\pos(540.160)}m 0 0 l 136 0 l 136 200 l 0 200
Dialogue: 1.1:11:38.64.1:11:42.60.Default.Screen.0.0.0..{\fad(167.1)\an5\fnTimes New Roman\fs14\fscy140\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(540.160)}Star\NReligious Group\NRepresentative\N{\fs30}Shigeru\NSonoda
Dialogue: 0.1:11:40.68.1:11:42.60.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..I'll even throw in a bonus.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:42.89.1:11:44.77.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Thank you. Founder.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:44.77.1:11:46.10.Default.Toji.0.0.0..You're so generous.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:46.10.1:11:48.19.Default.Kong.0.0.0..He's not the founder.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:48.19.1:11:49.19.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:11:50.40.1:11:51.81.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0.1:11:51.81.1:11:55.57.Default.Kong.0.0.0..I know it was a necessary expense. \Nbut you've already helped us out a lot. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:55.92.1:11:58.24.Default.Kong.0.0.0..I thought you'd complain a bit more.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:59.83.1:12:03.53.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..We hired you for the assassination \Nexpecting that it would fail.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:03.53.1:12:05.49.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..Our Star Religious Group \Nwas founded in the Nara Era.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:05.49.1:12:08.71.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..when Tengen-sama began preaching
Dialogue: 0.1:12:08.71.1:12:11.08.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..about the moral foundation \Nof jujutsu sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:11.08.1:12:13.66.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..a minority. as Buddhism \Nspread throughout Japan.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:14.29.1:12:17.80.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..Jujutsu society and religious corporations \Nare at complete odds with each other.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:17.80.1:12:20.05.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..That strain is what gave birth
Dialogue: 0.1:12:20.05.1:12:24.39.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..to our modern Star Religious Group. \Nthe Time Vessel Association.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:24.39.1:12:27.81.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..That is also why we have devoted \Nourselves to remaining non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:28.38.1:12:31.65.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..Jujutsu sorcerers are granted \Nmany privileges above the law.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:31.65.1:12:34.57.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..but they're still fundamentally forbidden \Nto lay a hand on non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:34.98.1:12:37.61.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..However. the time had finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:38.07.1:12:41.86.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..The time of the taboo \Nrecorded in our scriptures!
Dialogue: 0.1:12:42.24.1:12:43.95.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..Our Star Religious Group has evolved to
Dialogue: 0.1:12:43.95.1:12:46.16.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..a monotheistic religion \Nworshiping one absolute god!
Dialogue: 0.1:12:46.16.1:12:50.21.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..And it was now time for our object of \Nworship to assimilate with that impurity!
Dialogue: 0.1:12:52.12.1:12:55.09.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..If our believers saw us simply sit back \Nand watch the assimilation happen.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:55.09.1:12:56.84.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..our Association would crumble.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:57.55.1:13:02.09.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..Yet if we took excessive action. \Njujutsu sorcerers would crush us.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:02.38.1:13:05.85.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..So we were truly desperate.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:05.85.1:13:08.06.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..And how did it all turn out?
Dialogue: 0.1:13:08.06.1:13:10.48.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..We thought we were going to lose everything.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:10.48.1:13:12.60.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..and now we have it all!
Dialogue: 0.1:13:12.90.1:13:16.07.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..Of course that would \Nloosen our purse strings.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:18.03.1:13:23.61.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Human society might be what crumbles \Nif Tengen-sama loses control. though.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:25.57.1:13:29.20.Default.Sonoda.0.0.0..If we should perish along with our star. \Nthen that is all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:40.86.1:13:44.26.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Were you referring to Okinawa \Nwhen you said they helped us?
Dialogue: 0.1:13:44.26.1:13:45.13.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:45.47.1:13:48.68.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Why didn't you kill the maid then?
Dialogue: 0.1:13:48.68.1:13:50.09.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I know I told you.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:50.32.1:13:53.81.Default.Toji.0.0.0.."Take her someplace far away. \Nand kill her at some point."
Dialogue: 0.1:13:54.35.1:13:58.57.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Because I had a good idea of what \Nyou were planning at the time.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:58.90.1:14:01.64.Default.Kong.0.0.0..I made the call that the relief \Nfrom the maid's successful rescue
Dialogue: 0.1:14:01.64.1:14:05.49.Default.Kong.0.0.0..would wear him down more than \Nheightened tensions from failure.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:05.99.1:14:11.44.Default.Kong.0.0.0..You often ignore the lines of communication \Nand toss out whatever I was planning. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:14:12.12.1:14:14.08.Default.Kong.0.0.0..It all worked out in the end.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:14.08.1:14:17.33.Default.Kong.0.0.0..And stop running your mediator ragged.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:17.33.1:14:20.09.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Yeah. but why Okinawa?
Dialogue: 0.1:14:22.09.1:14:24.38.Default.Kong.0.0.0..I had a laugh at that myself.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:24.38.1:14:27.55.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Normally. you'd use a car \Nto transport a captive. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:14:27.55.1:14:30.76.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Public transportation carries \Ntoo many risks. after all.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:31.14.1:14:35.31.Default.Kong.0.0.0..But get this. The president \Nowned his own private jet.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:35.94.1:14:38.19.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Even so...
Dialogue: 0.1:14:40.19.1:14:43.15.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Rich people think on a different scale. man.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:43.15.1:14:45.49.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Well. let's go eat with their money.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:45.49.1:14:48.12.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Take me to one of the \Nrestaurants you use for clients.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:49.08.1:14:50.12.Default.Kong.0.0.0..No way.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:50.12.1:14:52.12.Default.Kong.0.0.0..You never pay for a guy. anyway.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:53.58.1:14:55.91.Default.Kong.0.0.0..I've already decided I'll only see you
Dialogue: 0.1:14:55.91.1:14:59.13.Default.Kong.0.0.0..either for work or in Hell.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:16.30.1:15:17.35.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:15:20.44.1:15:23.15.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Hey. it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:24.40.1:15:25.65.Default.Toji.0.0.0..For real?
Dialogue: 0.1:15:25.90.1:15:27.61.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..For real. real.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:28.57.1:15:30.87.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I'm alive and kicking!
Dialogue: 0.1:15:31.28.1:15:33.06.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Reverse cursed technique!
Dialogue: 0.1:15:33.70.1:15:35.33.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Bingo!
Dialogue: 0.1:15:35.33.1:15:37.93.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..When you stabbed me through the throat.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:37.93.1:15:39.46.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I gave up on counterattacking
Dialogue: 0.1:15:39.46.1:15:42.29.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..and poured all my focus into \Nthe reverse cursed technique.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:42.92.1:15:44.96.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Cursed energy is negative energy.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:44.96.1:15:48.18.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..While it can enhance the body. \Nit can't regenerate it.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:48.18.1:15:52.76.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So you multiply that negative energy \Nagainst itself to create positive energy.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:52.76.1:15:54.52.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..That's the reverse cursed technique.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:54.52.1:15:56.35.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Easier said than done!
Dialogue: 0.1:15:56.35.1:15:58.72.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I hadn't been able to do \Nthat up until now myself!
Dialogue: 0.1:15:58.72.1:16:02.31.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..And I couldn't understand anything \Nthe one person who could do it said!
Dialogue: 0.1:16:00.56.1:16:02.31.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..{\an8}He's blabbing on and on...
Dialogue: 0.1:16:02.69.1:16:06.03.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..He's high.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:06.57.1:16:08.98.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..But I finally grasped it \Non the verge of death!
Dialogue: 0.1:16:08.98.1:16:10.98.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The true essence of cursed energy!
Dialogue: 0.1:16:10.98.1:16:14.58.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The reason you're going to lose is \Nbecause you didn't chop my head off.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:14.58.1:16:18.25.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..and because you didn't use that cursed \Ntool when you stabbed my head.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:18.75.1:16:20.25.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I'm going to lose?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:23.04.1:16:25.04.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Our fight is just getting started.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:25.42.1:16:27.46.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Oh? Is it?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:27.46.1:16:28.97.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Yeah...
Dialogue: 0.1:16:28.97.1:16:30.76.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Maybe so!
Dialogue: 0.1:16:44.11.1:16:45.65.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Cursed Technique Reversal:
Dialogue: 0.1:16:47.78.1:16:48.65.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Red.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:03.96.1:17:05.41.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Monster.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:12.55.1:17:14.26.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..No bones are broken.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:14.76.1:17:18.18.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..That shock wave was an \Napplication of Limitless.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:18.18.1:17:20.22.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..the cursed technique reversal. Red. huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:17:21.23.1:17:24.69.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..So he poured the positive energy generated \Nby the reverse cursed technique
Dialogue: 0.1:17:24.69.1:17:29.49.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..into the Limitless \Ntechnique ingrained into him.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:30.03.1:17:32.07.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..One. the power to stop:
Dialogue: 0.1:17:32.07.1:17:34.24.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..the neutral application \Nof the Limitless technique.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:35.67.1:17:37.91.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..Two. the power to attract:
Dialogue: 0.1:17:37.91.1:17:40.62.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..the amplified application of \Nthe Limitless technique. Blue.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:41.70.1:17:44.08.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..And three. the power to repel:
Dialogue: 0.1:17:44.08.1:17:45.92.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..the reversal of his cursed technique. Red.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:48.96.1:17:51.83.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..All things I can handle.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:53.80.1:17:54.80.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..Something's off.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:00.68.1:18:01.93.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..Something's off.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:04.96.1:18:06.94.Default.Toji.0.0.0..No. this is fine.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:09.23.1:18:10.48.Default.Toji.0.0.0..I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:30.66.1:18:32.97.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Sorry. Amanai.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:33.47.1:18:36.97.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..I'm not even angry over you right now.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:38.18.1:18:40.18.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..I bear no grudge against anyone.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:42.51.1:18:47.20.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..It's just that the world feels \Nso. so wonderful right now.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:04.44.1:19:07.46.Default.Gojo.0.0.0.."Throughout Heaven and Earth. \NI alone am the honored one."
Dialogue: 0.1:19:11.14.1:19:14.17.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..The merit of having a technique \Nthat's passed down for generations
Dialogue: 0.1:19:14.17.1:19:15.76.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..is having a user's manual.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:16.68.1:19:18.22.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..The demerit is that
Dialogue: 0.1:19:18.22.1:19:21.14.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..information about the\Ntechnique is easily leaked.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:21.14.1:19:24.10.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..You were a member of \Nthe Zen'in clan. weren't you?
Dialogue: 0.1:19:24.62.1:19:27.98.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..That's why you know so much \Nabout the Limitless technique.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:29.65.1:19:32.82.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..However. even in the Gojo clan.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:32.82.1:19:35.11.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..only a scant few know about this.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:46.18.1:19:48.21.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Take the amplified and the reversal.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:48.21.1:19:51.04.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..then smash together those \Ntwo different expressions
Dialogue: 0.1:19:51.08.1:19:53.71.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..of infinity to create and \Npush out imaginary mass.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:54.05.1:19:56.47.Italics.Gojo.0.0.0..Imaginary Technique: Purple.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:05.60.1:20:07.06.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..Something's off.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:08.69.1:20:10.98.Italics.Toji.0.0.0.."I refuse to do any work for free."
Dialogue: 0.1:20:11.31.1:20:14.61.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..Normally I would've said that \Nand hightailed it out of there.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:15.57.1:20:20.32.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..Yet the freshly awakened wielder of the \NLimitless technique was right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:20.86.1:20:23.95.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..He was probably the strongest jujutsu \Nsorcerer of the modern age.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:24.70.1:20:26.70.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..I wanted to reject him.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:26.70.1:20:28.79.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..I wanted to bring him to his knees.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:29.26.1:20:32.54.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..I wanted to take down the \Npinnacle of the jujutsu world
Dialogue: 0.1:20:32.54.1:20:34.17.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..and the Zen'in clan that rejected me.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:35.25.1:20:40.13.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..I twisted myself to try to affirm myself.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:41.43.1:20:44.18.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..That was the moment I lost.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:53.90.1:20:56.19.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..I thought you had abandoned that pride.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:57.48.1:21:03.78.Italics.Toji.0.0.0..I thought you had chosen to live without \Nrespecting yourself or anyone else.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:08.20.1:21:10.70.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Any last words?
Dialogue: 0.1:21:13.63.1:21:15.17.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Nah.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:26.56.1:21:28.77.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Two or three years from now.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:28.77.1:21:31.44.Default.Toji.0.0.0..my kid will be sold off to the Zen'in clan.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:32.23.1:21:34.10.Default.Toji.0.0.0..Do what you will with that.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:03.72.1:22:05.77.Default.Storage.0.0.0..Mommy!
Dialogue: 0.1:22:06.14.1:22:08.14.Default.Storage.0.0.0..Hug me!
Dialogue: 0.1:22:47.13.1:22:48.93.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You're late. Suguru.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:49.36.1:22:51.60.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..No. I guess you got here fast.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:52.03.1:22:55.89.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..There are several Star Religious \NGroup facilities in the city. after all.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:57.24.1:22:59.86.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru? Is that you?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:00.67.1:23:02.32.Default.Geto.0.0.0..What happened?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:02.86.1:23:04.99.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I see you already saw Shoko.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:05.42.1:23:07.41.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Yeah. she healed me.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:07.89.1:23:09.37.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:12.45.1:23:15.88.Default.Geto.0.0.0..No. me being safe doesn't \Nhelp anything here.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:16.24.1:23:17.80.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:17.80.1:23:19.25.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You're not at fault.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:20.26.1:23:21.38.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:21.88.1:23:25.51.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Suguru. should we kill these guys?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:26.28.1:23:29.22.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The way I feel right now. \NI doubt I'd feel anything about it.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:31.76.1:23:34.19.Default.Geto.0.0.0..No. There's no point.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:35.02.1:23:38.56.Default.Geto.0.0.0..It looks like there are only \Ncommon believers here.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:38.96.1:23:42.45.Default.Geto.0.0.0..The masterminds who know about our \Nworld have probably fled already.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:43.24.1:23:45.28.Default.Geto.0.0.0..And unlike with the bounty.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:45.28.1:23:47.99.Default.Geto.0.0.0..they won't be able to \Ntalk their way out of this.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:47.99.1:23:50.41.Default.Geto.0.0.0..The organization had \Nproblems to begin with.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:50.77.1:23:52.38.Default.Geto.0.0.0..It'll be dissolved soon enough.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:54.46.1:23:55.67.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..No point. huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:56.04.1:23:59.17.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Does there really need \Nto be any point to it?
Dialogue: 0.1:24:10.85.1:24:12.68.Default.Geto.0.0.0..It's very important that there is.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:13.35.1:24:16.31.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Especially for a jujutsu sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:19.48.1:24:21.48.Default.Screen.0.0.0..1 YEAR LATER\NAUGUST 2007
Dialogue: 0.1:24:22.47.1:24:24.32.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Here we go.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:29.18.1:24:30.95.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Yeah. it's working.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:30.95.1:24:33.78.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Ugh. what the heck was that?
Dialogue: 0.1:24:33.78.1:24:36.41.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Automatic selection of targets \Nfor your jujutsu technique?
Dialogue: 0.1:24:36.41.1:24:37.41.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Yup.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:37.41.1:24:40.55.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Though. to be precise. \NI'm the target for the technique.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:40.90.1:24:44.13.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I've automated what I used to do manually.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:44.13.1:24:45.92.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Now it can discern an object's danger level
Dialogue: 0.1:24:46.21.1:24:50.80.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..based on the strength of its cursed energy. \Nits mass. its velocity. and its shape.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:50.80.1:24:53.99.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I'd like to get it to discern poisons. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:53.99.1:24:55.97.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..but that's still proving difficult.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:55.97.1:24:58.61.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..This will allow me to keep \Nmy Limitless technique active
Dialogue: 0.1:24:58.61.1:25:01.11.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..almost perpetually with minimal resources.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:01.11.1:25:04.07.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Having it perpetually active \Nwill fry your brain.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:04.07.1:25:06.51.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..But I can also keep running \Nthe reverse cursed technique
Dialogue: 0.1:25:06.51.1:25:08.16.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..with the energy I generate on my own.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:08.16.1:25:10.70.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So I'm constantly giving it \Na fresh brain to work with.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:11.47.1:25:14.25.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I'd already been working on shortening \Nmy hand seals. That's nailed now. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:14.25.1:25:19.50.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So I can also activate multiple \Ninstances of Blue and Red simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:19.50.1:25:20.92.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The only remaining hurdles are
Dialogue: 0.1:25:20.92.1:25:23.67.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Domain Expansion and \Nteleportation over long distances.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:24.17.1:25:26.33.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I should be able to get \Nthat down if we set up
Dialogue: 0.1:25:26.33.1:25:29.17.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..some courses without any \Nobstacles in Jujutsu High.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:29.59.1:25:32.46.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Shoko. could you lend me some lab rats?
Dialogue: 0.1:25:32.46.1:25:33.73.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Uh...
Dialogue: 0.1:25:33.73.1:25:36.03.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru had become the "strongest."
Dialogue: 0.1:25:36.03.1:25:38.70.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Suguru. have you lost weight?
Dialogue: 0.1:25:38.70.1:25:39.78.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:25:40.14.1:25:43.14.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..He handled all of his missions alone.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:43.14.1:25:46.77.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..and Shoko was never sent out on \Ndangerous missions in the first place.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:47.21.1:25:50.63.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..which naturally meant I was sent \Non missions alone more often. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:51.03.1:25:52.83.Default.Geto.0.0.0..It's just heat fatigue.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:52.83.1:25:54.30.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:55.05.1:25:56.79.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Did you eat too much somen?
Dialogue: 0.1:25:58.28.1:26:00.73.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Things were busy that summer.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:02.04.1:26:05.05.Default.Screen.0.0.0..Episode 29\N{\fs30\fscy150}Premature Death
Dialogue: 0.1:26:05.79.1:26:09.34.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Likely spurred by the frequent \Ndisasters of the past year.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:10.05.1:26:12.43.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..cursed spirits were \Nspringing up like maggots.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:13.93.1:26:16.17.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Exorcise. absorb.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:16.17.1:26:17.55.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Over and over.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:18.14.1:26:19.04.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Exorcise.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:19.04.1:26:20.01.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Absorb.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:21.02.1:26:23.93.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..No one else understands \Nwhat cursed spirits taste like.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:24.37.1:26:27.77.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..It's like swallowing a dirty rag that's \Nbeen used to clean up shit and vomit.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:30.48.1:26:31.91.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Who am I doing this for?
Dialogue: 0.1:26:35.94.1:26:37.09.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Exorcise.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:37.09.1:26:37.91.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Absorb.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:38.89.1:26:42.26.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..Ever since that day. \NI've been telling myself.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:42.26.1:26:45.01.Italics.Geto.0.0.0.."What I witnessed isn't uncommon."
Dialogue: 0.1:26:45.01.1:26:48.94.Italics.Geto.0.0.0.."I understood the ugliness of the masses.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:48.94.1:26:53.34.Italics.Geto.0.0.0.."and still chose to be a \Njujutsu sorcerer to save others."
Dialogue: 0.1:27:02.79.1:27:03.90.Italics.Geto.0.0.0.."Don't waver."
Dialogue: 0.1:27:04.40.1:27:06.85.Italics.Geto.0.0.0.."Fulfill your duty as a \Nstrong jujutsu sorcerer."
Dialogue: 0.1:27:26.41.1:27:27.88.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Damn monkeys...
Dialogue: 0.1:27:31.30.1:27:32.58.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Geto-san!
Dialogue: 0.1:27:33.90.1:27:35.26.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Haibara...
Dialogue: 0.1:27:36.17.1:27:37.69.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Good work out there!
Dialogue: 0.1:27:38.13.1:27:39.51.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0.1:27:39.71.1:27:42.07.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Huh? No. I'd feel bad!
Dialogue: 0.1:27:42.07.1:27:43.05.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..But I'll take a cola!
Dialogue: 0.1:27:46.01.1:27:49.15.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..I'm going pretty far away \Nfor my mission tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:49.15.1:27:50.33.Default.Geto.0.0.0..That so?
Dialogue: 0.1:27:50.33.1:27:51.77.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Bring back souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:51.77.1:27:52.98.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Of course!
Dialogue: 0.1:27:52.98.1:27:56.02.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Do you prefer sweet stuff or salty stuff?
Dialogue: 0.1:27:56.80.1:28:00.66.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru might eat some. too. so... sweet. I guess?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:00.88.1:28:02.25.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Got it!
Dialogue: 0.1:28:06.15.1:28:07.23.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Haibara...
Dialogue: 0.1:28:07.70.1:28:11.29.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Do you think you can keep going as a \Njujutsu sorcerer? It's not too hard for you?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:12.78.1:28:14.13.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Well...
Dialogue: 0.1:28:15.23.1:28:19.01.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..I'm not really one to think \Nabout things too deeply.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:19.33.1:28:23.64.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..so it feels really good to be able to \Ngive my all to something I can actually do.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:25.57.1:28:26.70.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I see.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:27.59.1:28:28.70.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Yeah. it does.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:33.23.1:28:34.94.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Are you Geto-kun?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:35.81.1:28:38.51.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..What kind of woman is your type?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:40.02.1:28:41.50.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Who are you?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:42.28.1:28:44.68.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..I like girls who eat a lot!
Dialogue: 0.1:28:44.68.1:28:45.66.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Oh?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:45.66.1:28:47.16.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Haibara...
Dialogue: 0.1:28:47.16.1:28:49.09.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:49.09.1:28:50.85.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..She's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:50.85.1:28:53.17.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..I'm a great judge of character!
Dialogue: 0.1:28:53.38.1:28:56.01.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You say that while sitting next to me?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:57.47.1:28:58.57.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Yes!
Dialogue: 0.1:29:00.38.1:29:02.99.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..He was being sarcastic. you know.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:04.37.1:29:05.55.Default.Haibara.0.0.0..Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:06.69.1:29:08.15.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Your underclassman?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:08.15.1:29:10.28.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..He's cute. I like how frank he is.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:10.28.1:29:13.59.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I think he should be more \Nsuspicious of people as a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:13.59.1:29:17.32.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..So. are you not going to answer?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:17.80.1:29:20.56.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Please answer my question first.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:20.56.1:29:21.83.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Who are you?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:22.17.1:29:24.94.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Special-grade sorcerer Yuki Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:24.94.1:29:26.74.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..That ring any bells?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:27.53.1:29:29.01.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You're {\i1}her{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:29.01.1:29:31.58.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Oh. I like the sound of that! What do they say?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:32.70.1:29:35.69.Default.Geto.0.0.0..That you're a special-grade \Nwho never accepts any missions.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:35.69.1:29:38.97.Default.Geto.0.0.0..and you're a good-for-nothing \Nwho's been wandering around abroad.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:38.97.1:29:42.07.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..I hate Jujutsu High.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:42.01.1:29:42.97.Default.Geto.0.0.0..{\fad(425.0)\fnComic Sans MS\b1\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H474A49&\shad0\bord1\frz281.8\pos(110.666.92)}She's pouting...
Dialogue: 0.1:29:42.07.1:29:42.97.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..She's pouting.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:43.41.1:29:44.62.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:44.62.1:29:48.75.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Though it's true that I don't get along \Nwith Jujutsu High's policies.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:48.75.1:29:52.34.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..What they're doing is just treating symptoms.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:52.34.1:29:54.86.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..and I want to do something \Nto treat the cause.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:55.25.1:29:57.07.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Treat the cause?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:57.07.1:29:59.37.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Rather than hunt down cursed spirits.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:59.37.1:30:02.53.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..I want to create a world \Nwhere cursed spirits aren't born.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:05.29.1:30:07.16.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Care for a little lesson?
Dialogue: 0.1:30:07.63.1:30:10.15.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..What are cursed spirits to begin with?
Dialogue: 0.1:30:10.15.1:30:12.98.Default.Geto.0.0.0..They're creatures that take \Nshape when cursed energy
Dialogue: 0.1:30:12.98.1:30:16.29.Default.Geto.0.0.0..leaking from humans \Nbuilds up like sediment.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:16.29.1:30:18.15.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Excellent.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:18.15.1:30:22.55.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Now this means there are two ways to create \Na world where cursed spirits aren't born.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:22.55.1:30:26.49.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..One: Eliminate cursed energy from mankind.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:26.49.1:30:30.56.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Two: Make it possible for all of humanity \Nto control their cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:30.79.1:30:34.32.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..I thought number one had a \Npretty good chance of working.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:34.71.1:30:36.55.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..There was a model case for it. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:36.55.1:30:38.01.Default.Geto.0.0.0..A model case?
Dialogue: 0.1:30:38.01.1:30:40.28.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Someone you know well.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:40.28.1:30:41.90.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Toji Zen'in.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:42.80.1:30:45.34.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..I've seen plenty of cases \Nwhere a Heavenly Pact reduced
Dialogue: 0.1:30:45.34.1:30:48.26.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..a person's cursed energy to the \Nlevel of your average person.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:48.26.1:30:50.40.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..but you could search the \Nwhole world only to find
Dialogue: 0.1:30:50.40.1:30:53.05.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..he was the only case in which \Nthat cursed energy dropped to zero.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:54.01.1:30:57.48.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..That wasn't the only intriguing \Nthing about him. either.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:57.91.1:31:01.16.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Even though Zen'in Toji \Nhad zero cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:01.16.1:31:03.58.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..he was able to perceive cursed \Nspirits with his five senses.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:03.58.1:31:05.93.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..By completely casting aside cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:05.93.1:31:07.79.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..his body drew a hard line
Dialogue: 0.1:31:07.79.1:31:10.68.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..and actually gave him \Ngreat resistance to curses.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:10.91.1:31:12.78.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..He truly was superhuman.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:13.16.1:31:15.31.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..You shouldn't be ashamed of losing to him.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:16.24.1:31:20.23.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..I wanted to try studying him. \Nbut he turned me down.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:20.23.1:31:22.19.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..It was a real shame to lose him.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:22.69.1:31:25.16.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..And there aren't many people \Nwith Heavenly Pacts.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:25.16.1:31:27.85.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..so I'm currently favoring route number two.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:27.85.1:31:31.54.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..making it possible for all of humanity \Nto control their cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:32.38.1:31:33.54.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Did you know?
Dialogue: 0.1:31:34.02.1:31:36.49.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Cursed spirits aren't born from sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:37.44.1:31:40.35.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Of course. that excludes cases \Nwhere the jujutsu sorcerer
Dialogue: 0.1:31:40.35.1:31:42.14.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..turns themselves into a curse after death.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:42.75.1:31:47.29.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Compared to non-sorcerers. jujutsu sorcerers \Nleak extremely little cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:47.64.1:31:49.76.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..There's some variance based \Non the sorcerer's capacity
Dialogue: 0.1:31:49.76.1:31:52.06.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..and the amount of cursed \Nenergy their technique expends.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:52.38.1:31:54.66.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..but the main reason is their flow.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:54.66.1:31:59.02.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Jujutsu sorcerers circulate cursed \Nenergy through their own bodies well.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:59.02.1:32:00.95.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..To put it in rough. general terms.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:00.95.1:32:03.55.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..if all of mankind were jujutsu sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:03.55.1:32:05.29.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..curses wouldn't be born.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:06.50.1:32:10.79.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Then you could solve it simply \Nby killing all non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:12.82.1:32:14.24.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Geto-kun.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:15.21.1:32:17.12.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..That's possible.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:17.12.1:32:18.77.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0.1:32:20.01.1:32:23.80.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..I mean. that's probably \Nthe easiest way to achieve it.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:24.25.1:32:26.58.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Just keep culling non-sorcerers and
Dialogue: 0.1:32:26.58.1:32:30.00.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..force them to adapt into sorcerers \Nas a survival strategy.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:30.00.1:32:35.05.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..You would be forcing them to \Nevolve using fear and danger.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:35.05.1:32:37.81.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..the same way birds gained wings.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:37.81.1:32:41.85.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..But unfortunately. I'm not \Ncrazy enough to do that.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:41.85.1:32:45.07.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Do you hate non-sorcerers. Geto-kun?
Dialogue: 0.1:32:49.03.1:32:50.79.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:50.79.1:32:54.77.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I always thought jujutsu sorcery \Nexisted to protect non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:54.77.1:32:57.56.Default.Geto.0.0.0..But lately. the value of non-sorcerers
Dialogue: 0.1:32:57.56.1:33:00.11.Default.Geto.0.0.0..has been wavering in my mind.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:00.61.1:33:02.54.Default.Geto.0.0.0..The admirability of the weak...
Dialogue: 0.1:33:02.54.1:33:04.46.Default.Geto.0.0.0..The ugliness of the weak...
Dialogue: 0.1:33:04.46.1:33:07.97.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I find myself struggling to discern \Nthe difference and accept those things.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:08.43.1:33:10.30.Default.Geto.0.0.0..There's a part of me \Nthat despises non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:10.30.1:33:12.39.Default.Geto.0.0.0..and a part of me that wants to reject that part.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:12.39.1:33:14.97.Default.Geto.0.0.0..My vision for what lies at \Nthe end of the marathon game
Dialogue: 0.1:33:14.97.1:33:17.39.Default.Geto.0.0.0..of being a jujutsu sorcerer is so vague now
Dialogue: 0.1:33:17.94.1:33:20.13.Default.Geto.0.0.0..that I can't tell which \Nrepresents how I truly feel.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:21.12.1:33:23.41.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Neither one is how you truly feel.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:27.02.1:33:29.15.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..You're not at that stage yet.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:29.15.1:33:31.65.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..This part of you despising non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:31.65.1:33:33.91.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..and this part of you rejecting that.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:34.13.1:33:37.23.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..are both just possibilities \Nthat you're considering.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:37.66.1:33:39.90.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..It's up to you to choose which part
Dialogue: 0.1:33:39.90.1:33:42.52.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..becomes your true \Nfeelings from here on out.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:46.29.1:33:47.56.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..See you later.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:47.56.1:33:50.68.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..It's a shame I didn't get to \Ntalk to Gojo-kun. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:50.68.1:33:52.58.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..but it looks like I missed him today.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:53.05.1:33:56.41.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..I hope the three of us can all \Nget along as fellow special-grades.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:57.64.1:34:00.46.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'll pass that along to Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:01.03.1:34:03.70.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Oh. right. one last thing.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:03.70.1:34:06.59.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..You don't need to worry \Nabout the Star Plasma Vessel.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:06.59.1:34:10.24.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Either there was already another \NStar Plasma Vessel at the time.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:10.24.1:34:13.68.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..or a new Star Plasma Vessel \Nhas already been born.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:14.15.1:34:17.59.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Either way. Tengen is stable.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:21.69.1:34:22.96.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:23.98.1:34:26.85.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..Oh. I didn't get his type.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:29.61.1:34:34.35.Default.Nanami.0.0.0..It was supposed to be an easy mission to \Nexterminate a second-grade cursed spirit!
Dialogue: 0.1:34:39.09.1:34:39.97.Default.Nanami.0.0.0..Damn it!
Dialogue: 0.1:34:45.06.1:34:46.99.Default.Nanami.0.0.0..Their faith in Ubusunagami...
Dialogue: 0.1:34:49.06.1:34:51.03.Default.Nanami.0.0.0..That was a local deity.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:51.76.1:34:53.45.Default.Nanami.0.0.0..That was a first-grade case!
Dialogue: 0.1:34:56.45.1:34:59.25.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You need to rest for now. Nanami.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:59.61.1:35:01.70.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Satoru has taken up your mission.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:03.80.1:35:07.09.Default.Nanami.0.0.0..Can't we just leave everything \Nup to him alone at this point?
Dialogue: 0.1:35:08.89.1:35:11.71.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..This marathon game of being \Na jujutsu sorcerer...
Dialogue: 0.1:35:13.98.1:35:16.09.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..If the only thing waiting at the end
Dialogue: 0.1:35:17.89.1:35:21.27.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..is a mountain of our \Ncomrades' corpses. then...
Dialogue: 0.1:35:32.73.1:35:34.20.Default.Geto.0.0.0..What is this?
Dialogue: 0.1:35:34.20.1:35:35.89.Default.Man.0.0.0..What. you ask?
Dialogue: 0.1:35:35.89.1:35:38.95.Default.Man.0.0.0..These two are responsible \Nfor the latest incidents. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:35:41.63.1:35:42.71.Default.Geto.0.0.0..No. they're not.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:49.42.1:35:51.38.Default.Man.0.0.0..These two are crazy!
Dialogue: 0.1:35:51.73.1:35:55.29.Default.Man.0.0.0..They used their mysterious powers \Nto attack the villagers!
Dialogue: 0.1:35:55.79.1:35:58.93.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I've already exterminated \Nthe cause of those incidents.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:58.93.1:36:02.05.Default.Woman.0.0.0..My granddaughter was nearly \Nkilled by these two. too!
Dialogue: 0.1:36:02.05.1:36:03.18.Default.Nanako.0.0.0..That's because she—
Dialogue: 0.1:36:03.18.1:36:05.17.Default.Woman.0.0.0..Shut up. you monsters!
Dialogue: 0.1:36:05.17.1:36:07.22.Default.Woman.0.0.0..Your parents were just as bad!
Dialogue: 0.1:36:07.22.1:36:10.61.Default.Curse.0.0.0..{\an8}It... It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:07.23.1:36:10.61.Default.Woman.0.0.0..I knew we should have killed you \Ntwo when you were babies!
Dialogue: 0.1:36:13.06.1:36:15.32.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..This part of you despising non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:15.32.1:36:16.94.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..and this part of you rejecting that..
Dialogue: 0.1:36:17.37.1:36:19.66.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0..It's up to you to choose which part...
Dialogue: 0.1:36:20.25.1:36:24.12.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Everyone. shall we step \Noutside for a moment?
Dialogue: 0.1:36:24.12.1:36:26.62.Default.Tsukumo.0.0.0.....becomes your true \Nfeelings from here on out.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:32.01.1:36:33.41.Default.Woman.0.0.0..What?!
Dialogue: 0.1:36:34.05.1:36:34.54.Default.Man.0.0.0..Why?!
Dialogue: 0.1:36:37.05.1:36:38.40.Default.Woman.0.0.0..No!
Dialogue: 0.1:36:52.36.1:36:54.69.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..112 RESIDENTS OF THE VILLAGE WERE KILLED. \NAFTER WHICH A FIRE...\NBY THE TIME JUJUTSU HIGH INVESTIGATED\NON 23RD SEPTEMBER
Dialogue: 0.1:36:54.69.1:36:57.07.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..INVESTIGATIONS CONFIRMED THAT ALL 112\NWERE KILLED BY A CURSED SPIRIT. WHICH THE RESIDUALS REVEALED TO BE THE WORK\NOF SUGURU GETO'S CURSED MANIUPLATION
Dialogue: 0.1:36:57.07.1:37:00.45.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0.....SENTENCED TO DEATH.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:05.73.1:37:06.65.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:37:07.46.1:37:09.58.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:09.58.1:37:12.60.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Suguru killed everyone in the village and—
Dialogue: 0.1:37:11.66.1:37:13.51.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I heard you the first time.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:13.51.1:37:15.88.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..That's why I said. "Huh?"
Dialogue: 0.1:37:17.23.1:37:20.77.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Suguru's old home was already \Nan empty husk. as well.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:21.22.1:37:24.97.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Though. from the bloodstains and residuals. he most likely killed his parents. too—
Dialogue: 0.1:37:24.97.1:37:26.13.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Like hell he did!
Dialogue: 0.1:37:26.13.1:37:27.48.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Satoru.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:27.48.1:37:30.98.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..I don't understand what's going on. either.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:39.74.1:37:40.86.Default - Copy.Sign.0.0.0..HUH? A HIGH SCHOOLER?
Dialogue: 0.1:37:44.74.1:37:46.39.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Need a light?
Dialogue: 0.1:37:48.33.1:37:49.28.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:50.33.1:37:51.79.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..It's the criminal.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:52.13.1:37:53.54.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Need something?
Dialogue: 0.1:37:53.54.1:37:55.84.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Just testing my luck. I guess.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:57.29.1:37:58.73.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..I'll go ahead and ask...
Dialogue: 0.1:37:58.73.1:38:00.38.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Any chance the charges are false?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:00.58.1:38:02.85.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Nope. Unfortunately not.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:03.50.1:38:06.29.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..I'll ask further. then. Why?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:06.72.1:38:08.84.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'm going to create a world \Nof only jujutsu sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:09.96.1:38:11.98.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:11.98.1:38:13.82.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'm not a child.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:13.82.1:38:17.20.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'm not holding out hope \Nthat everyone will understand.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:17.61.1:38:20.88.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Sulking over the idea that \Nno one will understand you
Dialogue: 0.1:38:20.88.1:38:23.37.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..sounds pretty childish to me. though.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:23.37.1:38:24.98.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Hey. Gojo?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:25.32.1:38:26.54.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..I found Geto.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:27.07.1:38:28.66.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..Yeah. Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:29.82.1:38:32.12.Default.Shoko.0.0.0..No way. I don't want to get killed.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:41.41.1:38:43.84.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Explain yourself. Suguru.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:48.26.1:38:50.17.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You already heard from Shoko. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:50.50.1:38:52.81.Default.Geto.0.0.0..That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:52.81.1:38:55.31.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So you're just going to kill \Neveryone who's not a sorcerer?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:56.06.1:38:57.32.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Even your parents?!
Dialogue: 0.1:38:57.32.1:39:00.37.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I can't allow my parents \Nto be a special exception.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:00.37.1:39:03.57.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Besides. those people \Naren't my family anymore.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:03.57.1:39:05.44.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..That's not what I was asking!
Dialogue: 0.1:39:05.80.1:39:08.62.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I thought we weren't allowed to \Nkill when there's no point to it!
Dialogue: 0.1:39:09.32.1:39:11.77.Default.Geto.0.0.0..There is a point to it. Significance. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:11.77.1:39:13.16.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Even a great cause.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:13.16.1:39:14.65.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..There's not!
Dialogue: 0.1:39:14.65.1:39:18.23.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You're going to kill all non-sorcerers and \Ncreate a world of only jujutsu sorcerers?!
Dialogue: 0.1:39:18.23.1:39:19.67.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You know that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0.1:39:20.38.1:39:22.42.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..There's no point in chipping away bit by bit
Dialogue: 0.1:39:22.42.1:39:24.18.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..at something you can't possibly do!
Dialogue: 0.1:39:25.87.1:39:27.18.Default.Geto.0.0.0..How arrogant.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:28.15.1:39:29.31.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:39:29.81.1:39:32.65.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You could do it. couldn't you. Satoru?
Dialogue: 0.1:39:35.41.1:39:37.48.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Yet you would try to convince someone else
Dialogue: 0.1:39:38.07.1:39:42.40.Default.Geto.0.0.0..that it's impossible to do \Nsomething that's possible for you?
Dialogue: 0.1:39:45.61.1:39:49.13.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Are you the strongest \Nbecause you're Satoru Gojo?
Dialogue: 0.1:39:49.13.1:39:51.69.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Or does being the strongest \Nmake you Satoru Gojo?
Dialogue: 0.1:39:51.69.1:39:53.82.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0.1:39:53.82.1:39:56.57.Default.Geto.0.0.0..If I were able to become you.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:57.04.1:40:00.62.Default.Geto.0.0.0..this foolish ideal would become a lot \Nmore grounded and real. don't you think?
Dialogue: 0.1:40:02.37.1:40:04.25.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I've decided how I'll live my life.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:04.25.1:40:07.13.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Now it's just a matter of doing \Nthe best I can to achieve that.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:16.60.1:40:18.34.Default.Geto.0.0.0..If you want to kill me. then kill me.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:20.35.1:40:22.10.Default.Geto.0.0.0..There would be a point to that.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:42.10.1:40:44.17.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Why didn't you pursue him?
Dialogue: 0.1:40:47.61.1:40:50.01.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You're actually asking me that?
Dialogue: 0.1:40:52.05.1:40:53.55.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Nah. it's fine.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:53.87.1:40:55.13.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..My bad.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:58.89.1:41:01.50.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Sensei. I'm strong. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:41:01.50.1:41:04.29.Default.Yaga.0.0.0..Yeah. brazenly so.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:06.08.1:41:09.71.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..But apparently. it's not good enough \Nfor just me to be strong.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:10.35.1:41:12.21.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The only ones I can save
Dialogue: 0.1:41:12.21.1:41:14.94.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..are those who are already ready \Nto be saved by another.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:19.77.1:41:22.57.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I thought the Star Religious Group \Nwas already dissolved.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:22.57.1:41:25.40.Default.Kong.0.0.0..It's a different group. \Nbut their roots are the same.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:25.40.1:41:28.29.Default.Kong.0.0.0..They're claiming they just bought \Nthe existing space as-is.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:28.29.1:41:29.37.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Don't like it?
Dialogue: 0.1:41:29.37.1:41:33.17.Default.Geto.0.0.0..No. it doesn't matter. as long as \NI can gather curses and money.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:33.34.1:41:35.97.Default.Kong.0.0.0..Are you really going out dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0.1:41:35.97.1:41:38.86.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Why not? A little showmanship is important.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:39.25.1:41:40.87.Default.Nanako.0.0.0..Geto-sama...
Dialogue: 0.1:41:40.87.1:41:42.25.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:42.70.1:41:43.93.Default.Geto.0.0.0..They're all there. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:41:43.93.1:41:47.18.Default.Kong.0.0.0..All the branch directors. \Nall the representatives. and the president.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:47.18.1:41:49.46.Default.Kong.0.0.0..All the big donors. as well.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:52.79.1:41:57.89.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Test. test. Sorry for the wait. everyone.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:57.89.1:41:59.77.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Now. I'll keep this brief.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:00.13.1:42:03.77.Default.Geto.0.0.0..From this moment onward. \Nthis organization belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:04.27.1:42:05.86.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I'll be changing the name. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:05.86.1:42:08.65.Default.Geto.0.0.0..so everyone. please be sure to follow me.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:08.65.1:42:10.53.Default - Copy..0.0.0..MANY OBJECTED
Dialogue: 0.1:42:10.66.1:42:12.73.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Now. that's not good.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:13.29.1:42:14.67.Default.Geto.0.0.0..I know!
Dialogue: 0.1:42:14.67.1:42:17.65.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Sonoda-san. if you wouldn't mind. \Nplease come to the stage.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:18.59.1:42:20.41.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Yes! You there!
Dialogue: 0.1:42:21.09.1:42:23.08.Default.Geto.0.0.0..Now. once again.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:23.61.1:42:25.09.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..I hate monkeys.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:25.09.1:42:27.03.Default.Geto.0.0.0..You obey me now...
Dialogue: 0.1:42:27.25.1:42:29.52.Italics.Geto.0.0.0..That's the true feeling I chose.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:30.18.1:42:31.57.Default.Geto.0.0.0.....monkeys.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:34.12.1:42:37.02.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You're Megumi Fushiguro-kun. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:39.15.1:42:40.57.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..Who are you?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:40.57.1:42:42.86.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..And what's with that weird face?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:44.38.1:42:46.79.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You look just like him. is all.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:48.15.1:42:49.69.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..My own issue.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:50.06.1:42:51.97.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So listen. About your dad...
Dialogue: 0.1:42:51.97.1:42:55.04.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..He's from this big shot jujutsu \Nsorcerer family called the Zen'in.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:55.04.1:42:57.21.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..but they're such scumbags \Nthey make even me sick.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:57.21.1:43:00.29.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..and that's why your dad left \Nthe family and had you.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:00.29.1:43:02.83.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Now. you're one of the \Nones who can see things.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:02.83.1:43:04.33.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..so you're privileged there. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:43:04.88.1:43:07.58.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..You've noticed the power \Nwithin yourself. too. yeah?
Dialogue: 0.1:43:08.13.1:43:10.77.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..The Zen'in clan just loves strong powers.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:10.77.1:43:13.97.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Most become aware of their cursed \Ntechniques around 4-6 years old.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:13.97.1:43:16.44.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So it's the perfect timing to sell a kid off.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:16.69.1:43:18.35.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So. Megumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:18.35.1:43:22.69.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..you were the ultimate card that your dad \Nkept on hand against the Zen'in clan.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:22.69.1:43:24.39.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Pisses you off. doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0.1:43:24.39.1:43:28.28.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So. about that dad of yours. I ki—
Dialogue: 0.1:43:27.28.1:43:28.28.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..I don't care.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:28.87.1:43:31.65.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..I have no interest in where \Nhe is or what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:31.65.1:43:34.54.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..I haven't even seen him in years. \Nso I don't remember what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:34.97.1:43:37.16.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..Though I get the general idea \Nfrom what you just said.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:37.83.1:43:40.99.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..Tsumiki's mother hasn't come home \Nfor a while now. either.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:40.99.1:43:43.35.Default.Tsumiki.0.0.0..Ah. Megumi's home!
Dialogue: 0.1:43:43.79.1:43:46.09.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..That means they're finished with us.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:46.09.1:43:48.59.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..and they're off enjoying \Nthemselves elsewhere. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:43:49.88.1:43:52.58.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Are you really a first grader?
Dialogue: 0.1:43:53.18.1:43:54.49.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Well. whatever.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:54.49.1:43:57.61.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..If you ever want to know about \Nyour father. you can ask me.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:57.61.1:43:59.42.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Hup.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:59.42.1:44:01.89.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I think it'll be pretty interesting to hear.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:01.89.1:44:03.61.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Now. on to the main point.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:03.61.1:44:05.28.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0.1:44:05.28.1:44:06.97.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Do you want to go to the Zen'in clan?
Dialogue: 0.1:44:07.89.1:44:09.45.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..What will happen to Tsumiki?
Dialogue: 0.1:44:09.77.1:44:13.53.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..If I go there. will Tsumiki be able to \Nfind happiness? It all depends on that.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:13.53.1:44:15.81.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..No. A hundred percent no.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:15.81.1:44:17.63.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I can say that with certainty.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:20.98.1:44:22.49.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Okay!
Dialogue: 0.1:44:23.34.1:44:25.25.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Leave the rest to me. then.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:27.11.1:44:30.37.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..I might need you to push yourself a bit. though.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:30.69.1:44:32.05.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..So do your best.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:32.46.1:44:34.07.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Get stronger.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:34.92.1:44:37.48.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Strong enough to keep up with me.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:38.88.1:44:42.80.Default - Copy.Screen.0.0.0..OCTOBER 19. 2018
Dialogue: 0.1:44:44.08.1:44:45.52.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..Gojo-sensei.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:45.52.1:44:47.48.Default.Yuji.0.0.0..So even Sensei sleeps. huh?
Dialogue: 0.1:44:47.48.1:44:49.99.Default.Nobara.0.0.0..Of course he does. \NWhat kind of nonsense is that?
Dialogue: 0.1:44:49.99.1:44:51.35.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..Gojo-sensei!
Dialogue: 0.1:44:52.40.1:44:53.93.Default.Yuji.0.0.0..Oh. he's awake.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:53.93.1:44:56.37.Default.Nobara.0.0.0..Hey. that's one of those \Nexpensive chairs. isn't it?
Dialogue: 0.1:44:56.37.1:44:59.33.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..Please don't fall asleep \Nafter summoning all of us here.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:00.81.1:45:02.73.Default.Yuji.0.0.0..Hey. no fair! I get it next. got it?!
Dialogue: 0.1:45:02.73.1:45:04.65.Default.Yuji.0.0.0..Hey! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0.1:45:04.65.1:45:05.96.Default.Megumi.0.0.0..What are you smiling about?
Dialogue: 0.1:45:04.65.1:45:07.84.Default.Yuji.0.0.0..{\an8}Don't be mean! Move it!
Dialogue: 0.1:45:07.84.1:45:08.83.Default.Gojo.0.0.0..Nothing.
